ng:0px 0px 6px;border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:solid;border-color:#DCDCDC;border-image:initial;vertical-align:baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;font-family:微软雅黑;background:#F6F5F5;font-size:14px;color:#666666;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;\">\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:10px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;\">\n		<p>\n			<br />\n		</p>\n		<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\n			<strong>行程安排</strong> \n		</div>\n		<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\n			7点：指定地点集合\n		</div>\n		<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\n			7点10：准时出发\n		</div>\n		<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\n			去程：成都出发到邛崃楠木溪行程110公里左右，行车时间预计2.-2.5小时，中途设一个休息点\n		</div>\n		<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\n			返程：返程途中不设休息点，突发情况有需要和领队协商。返程地点和上车地点一致，中途在司机可以停靠的公交站，有3次停靠机会，具体停靠和车上领队和司机协商。\n		</div>\n		<p>\n			<br />\n		</p>\n	</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"hdxq\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;border-width:1px 1px 3px;border-style:solid;border-color:#DCDCDC #DCDCDC #FF8800;border-image:initial;vertical-align:baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;font-family:微软雅黑;height:40px;line-height:40px;background:#F6F5F5;position:relative;color:#666666;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;\">\n	<h2 class=\"detailh2\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px 20px;font-size:14px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;float:left;display:inline;color:#4F4F4F;\">\n		<img style=\"height:20px;vertical-align:middle;\" src=\"/web/tubiao/6.png\" /><span class=\"icon-bright\" style=\"margin:0px 10px 0px 0px;padding:0px;border:0px;vertical-align:middle;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;background-image:url(\" background-repeat:no-repeat;display:inline-block;width:16px;height:16px;background-position:-217px=\"\" -80px;\"=\"\"> </span><span>活动详情</span> \n	</h2>\n</div>\n<div style=\"margin:0px 0px 15px;padding:0px 0px 6px;border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:solid;border-color:#DCDCDC;border-image:initial;vertical-align:baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;font-family:微软雅黑;background:#F6F5F5;font-size:14px;color:#666666;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;\">\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:10px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;\">\n		<p>\n			<br />\n		</p>\n		<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:12px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑, Helvetica, STHeiTi, sans-seri;font-size:16px;white-space:normal;\">\n			【楠木溪介绍】\n		</p>\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:12px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑, Helvetica, STHeiTi, sans-seri;font-size:16px;white-space:normal;\">\n			楠木溪位于邛崃高何镇高兴村，距离成都110公里，距天台山风景区约8公里。楠木溪是一条约4公里长的狭长河谷，苍翠的青山，清澈甘洌的山泉带着阵阵凉风长年不息地流淌着。\n		</p>\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:12px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑, Helvetica, STHeiTi, sans-seri;font-size:16px;white-space:normal;\">\n			<img src=\"http://tubu.juntong.me/upload/201708250154197512.png\" style=\"max-width:600px !important;\" /> \n		</p>\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:12px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑, Helvetica, STHeiTi, sans-seri;font-size:16px;white-space:normal;\">\n			<img src=\"http://tubu.juntong.me/upload/201708250154365294.jpg\" style=\"max-width:600px !important;\" /> \n		</p>\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:12px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑, Helvetica, STHeiTi, sans-seri;font-size:16px;white-space:normal;\">\n			<img src=\"http://tubu.juntong.me/upload/201708250155066299.jpg\" style=\"max-width:600px !important;\" /> \n		</p>\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:12px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑, Helvetica, STHeiTi, sans-seri;font-size:16px;white-space:normal;\">\n			处于城市喧嚣中的你 ——想不想在幽静的山间溪水边，借居山中朴素人家，闻鸟语花香、听鸡犬相鸣，沿溪插水，寻觅萤火虫的踪迹.........\n		</p>\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:12px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑, Helvetica, STHeiTi, sans-seri;font-size:16px;white-space:normal;\">\n			<img src=\"http://tubu.juntong.me/upload/201708250157351183.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:600px !important;\" /> \n		</p>\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:12px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑, Helvetica, STHeiTi, sans-seri;font-size:16px;white-space:normal;\">\n			<img src=\"http://tubu.juntong.me/upload/201708250157392129.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:600px !important;\" /> \n		</p>\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:12px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑, Helvetica, STHeiTi, sans-seri;font-size:16px;white-space:normal;\">\n			这里群峰耸峙，谷中瀑布飞泻、溪流潺潺、叠泉幽潭、错落有致，颇具国画山水之韵致。\n		</p>\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:12px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑, Helvetica, STHeiTi, sans-seri;font-size:16px;white-space:normal;\">\n			<img src=\"http://tubu.juntong.me/upload/201708250158418500.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:600px !important;\" /> \n		</p>\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:12px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑, Helvetica, STHeiTi, sans-seri;font-size:16px;white-space:normal;\">\n			<img src=\"http://tubu.juntong.me/upload/201708250158485044.png\" style=\"max-width:600px !important;\" /> \n		</p>\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:12px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑, Helvetica, STHeiTi, sans-seri;font-size:16px;white-space:normal;\">\n			一条从邛崃山脉中缓缓流淌出的溪流，蜿蜒曲折，清澈见底。四周青山环抱，绿树成荫。溪流两岸，山势平缓，植被浓密。这里，气候宜人，空气清新……\n		</p>\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:12px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑, Helvetica, STHeiTi, sans-seri;font-size:16px;white-space:normal;\">\n			<img src=\"http://tubu.juntong.me/upload/201708250203156440.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:600px !important;\" /> \n		</p>\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:12px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑, Helvetica, STHeiTi, sans-seri;font-size:16px;white-space:normal;\">\n			<img src=\"http://tubu.juntong.me/upload/2017082502031895.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:600px !important;\" /> \n		</p>\n		<p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:12px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑, Helvetica, STHeiTi, sans-seri;font-size:16px;white-space:normal;\">\n			这里民风纯朴，田园风光优美抒情。既有世外桃园般的陶翁诗歌意境，又有王维清远诗风的宁静致远之韵味。聆旷谷鸟语，看花开花落，心享山水田园，怡情逸志其乐融融。是游客休闲养生圣地。\n		</p>\n		<p>\n			<br />\n		</p>\n	</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"ydxz\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;border-width:1px 1px 3px;border-style:solid;border-color:#DCDCDC #DCDCDC #FF8800;border-image:initial;vertical-align:baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;font-family:微软雅黑;height:40px;line-height:40px;background:#F6F5F5;position:relative;color:#666666;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;\">\n	<h2 class=\"detailh2\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px 20px;font-size:14px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;float:left;display:inline;color:#4F4F4F;\">\n		<img style=\"height:20px;vertical-align:middle;\" src=\"/web/tubiao/5.png\" /><span class=\"icon-bright\" style=\"margin:0px 10px 0px 0px;padding:0px;border:0px;vertical-align:middle;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;background-image:url(\" background-repeat:no-repeat;display:inline-block;width:16px;height:16px;background-position:-217px=\"\" -80px;\"=\"\"> </span><span>预订须知</span> \n	</h2>\n</div>\n<div style=\"margin:0px 0px 15px;padding:0px 0px 6px;border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:solid;border-color:#DCDCDC;border-image:initial;vertical-align:baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;font-family:微软雅黑;background:#F6F5F5;font-size:14px;color:#666666;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;\">\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:10px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;\">\n		<p>\n			<br />\n		</p>\n		<div style=\"text-align:left;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#666666;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;background-color:#F6F5F5;outline:none !important;\">\n			<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin: