66666;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;background-color:#F6F5F5;\">2、其他个人消费。<br />\n			<div style=\"color:#666666;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;background-color:#F6F5F5;outline:none !important;\">\n				<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-weight:700;outline:none !important;\"><br />\n【报名须知】</span> \n			</div>\n			<p>\n				在线报名：活动页面“选择批次”，然后点击“立即报名”进行网上报名，按照要求提交有效信息。<br />\n退费须知：成功报名后不支持退款，如需退款在活动<span style=\"color:#666666;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;background-color:#F6F5F5;\">前</span>36小时找客服申请退款，36小时内因个人原因退出不予退费。<br />\n客服微信：tunaer-club<br />\n客服电话：13540139792<br />\nQQ群：256606057<br />\n徒哪儿微信公众号：cdtunaer<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color:#666666;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;background-color:#F6F5F5;\"><strong>以下人员请勿报名:</strong><br />\n参加活动的人员须身体健康，户外活动可能对身体和精神方面都有严格的要求，可能远离救助和医疗服务，凡隐瞒自己疾病，给团队和个人造成损失者，一切后果自付，并负相应法律责任。(1)传染性疾病患者，如传染性肝炎、活动期肺结核、伤寒等传染病人;(2)心血管疾病患者，如严重高血压、心功能不全、心肌缺氧、心肌梗塞等病人;(3)脑血管疾病患者，如脑栓塞、脑出血、脑肿瘤等病人;(4)呼吸系统疾病患者，如肺气肿、肺心病等病人;(5)精神病患者，如癫痫及各种精神病人;(6)严重贫血病患者，如血红蛋白量水平在50克/升以下的病人;(7)大中型手术的恢复期病患者;(8)孕妇及行动不便者;(9)其他不适合出去旅行的疾病。</span> \n			</p>\n</span> \n		</div>\n		<div style=\"text-align:left;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;background-color:#F6F5F5;color:#333333;font-family:&quot;outline:none !important;\">\n		</div>\n	</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"qtxx\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;border-width:1px 1px 3px;border-style:solid;border-color:#DCDCDC #DCDCDC #FF8800;border-image:initial;vertical-align:baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;font-family:微软雅黑;height:40px;line-height:40px;background:#F6F5F5;position:relative;color:#666666;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;\">\n	<h2 class=\"detailh2\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px 20px;font-size:14px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;float:left;display:inline;color:#4F4F4F;\">\n		<img style=\"height:20px;vertical-align:middle;\" src=\"/web/tubiao/3.png\" /><span class=\"icon-bright\" style=\"margin:0px 10px 0px 0px;padding:0px;border:0px;vertical-align:middle;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;background-image:url(\" background-repeat:no-repeat;display:inline-block;width:16px;height:16px;background-position:-217px=\"\" -80px;\"=\"\"> </span><span>其他信息</span> \n	</h2>\n</div>\n<div style=\"margin:0px 0px 15px;padding:0px 0px 6px;border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:solid;border-color:#DCDCDC;border-image:initial;vertical-align:baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;font-family:微软雅黑;background:#F6F5F5;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;\">\n	<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\n		<div style=\"text-indent:0px;\">\n			<span style=\"text-indent:18pt;\"> \n			<div style=\"text-indent:0px;\">\n				<span style=\"color:#E53333;text-indent:18pt;\"><span style=\"color:#666666;\"> \n				<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;background-color:#F6F5F5;outline:none !important;\">\n					<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-weight:700;text-indent:18pt;outline:none !important;\"><br />\n【活动装备】</span> \n				</div>\n<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;background-color:#F6F5F5;text-indent:18pt;outline:none !important;\"> \n				<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;text-indent:0px;\">\n					<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;text-indent:18pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;color:#666666;\">1、饮用水（建议使用保暖水壶，夏季推荐1.5L，冬季1L）</span><br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\" />\n</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;text-indent:18pt;color:#666666;\">2、路餐（熟食、凉菜、水果，其次牛奶面包，最次方便米饭）<br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\" />\n</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;text-indent:18pt;color:#666666;\">3、户外背包，徒步鞋、登山鞋都行（能防水的最好），登山杖（尽量带上）<br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\" />\n</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;text-indent:18pt;color:#666666;\">4、户外服装（冲锋衣裤+速干衣+手套等）<br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\" />\n</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;text-indent:18pt;color:#666666;\">（户外天气多变，请尽量带上雨具，为更好的保护你的手机、证件，建议准备1个防水袋）<br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\" />\n</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;text-indent:18pt;color:#666666;\">5、感冒药、肠胃药、晕车药、维它命、创可贴，可准备些葡萄糖口服液补充能量<br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\" />\n</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;text-indent:18pt;color:#666666;\">6、保湿霜＋护手霜＋护唇（MM必备）<br />\n<span style=\"color:#333333;font-weight:700;text-indent:18pt;\"><br />\n【活动声明】</span></span> \n				</div>\n</span> \n				<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;text-align:center;white-space:normal;background-color:#F6F5F5;outline:none !important;\">\n					<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">\n						<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;text-indent:18pt;\"> \n						<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;text-align:left;\">\n							<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;\">我们是一群喜欢户外运动的</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;\">AA</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;\">制徒友，所有领队有义务保护好大家安全、同时也希望大家听从领队的安排。</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;color:#E53333;text-indent:18pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;color:#666666;\">徒步不等同于旅游。徒友们在参加活动的过程过中，应遵循徒哪儿网活动规则。<br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\" />\n</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;\">一、安全第一；上车请系好安全带，徒步中遇见危险地段请呼叫领队，</span> \n						</div>\n						<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">\n							<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;\"> \n							<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;text-align:left;text-indent:0px;\">\n								<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;text-indent:18pt;\">二、徒友们不争吵，不在微信群里语言重伤他人。</span> \n							</div>\n</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;text-indent:18pt;\"> \n							<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;text-indent:0px;\">\n								<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;text-align:left;\">\n									<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#E53333;outline:none !important;\">\n										<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;\">三、参加活动的徒友们请按时遵守集合时间；超出规定时间可以等待</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;\">5</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;\">分钟，如特殊情况最多等待</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;\">10</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;\">分钟将发车，反程同</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;\">样遵守时间，没有赶上车的徒友将不在退款。</span> \n									</div>\n<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;text-indent:18pt;\"> \n									<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;text-indent:0px;\">\n										<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;\">四、请徒友们严格按照分车信息（车牌号、车辆编号）上车。<br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\" />\n</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;\">五、不准在车上吃东西，吃东西请提前在车下吃好，以免车上气味过大。<br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\" />\n</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;\">六、不准在临近发车时上厕所。<br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\" />\n</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;\">七、徒友回城上车请原车原位就坐，不得调换车位及车辆。<br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\" />\n</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;text-indent:18pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;color:#666666;\">八、爱护环境，不乱扔垃圾，不破坏植物，养成好的习惯，鼓励拾捡垃圾。做到“只留下你的脚印，只带走你的回忆”。<br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\" />\n</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;text-indent:18pt;color:#E53333;\">九、</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;text-indent:18pt;color:#E53333;\">小孩报名参加活动同样占车位，不能由大人抱着</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;text-indent:18pt;color:#E53333;\">。</span> \n									</div>\n</span> \n								</div>\n							</div>\n</span> \n						</div>\n<br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\" />\n</span> \n					</div>\n				</div>\n				<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;background-color:#F6F5F5;font-family:&quot;outline:none !important;\">\n					<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;font-weight:700;outline:none !important;\">【请徒友们注意】</span> \n				</div>\n<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;text-align:center;white-space:normal;color:#666666;background-color:#F6F5F5;outline:none !important;\"> \n				<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;text-align:left;\">\n					<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">1、由于户外活动具有一定的风险，可能对身体素质和精神状态方面有一定的要求，可能远离救助和医疗服务。请参与者仔细阅读、谨慎报名，如报名成功、对报名者均视为有完全民事责任。故患有：传染性疾病(如传染性肝炎、活动期肺炎、伤寒等）；心血管疾病（如严重高血压、心功能不全、心肌缺氧、心肌梗塞等病人），脑血管疾病患者（如脑栓塞、脑出血、脑肿瘤等病人）；呼吸系统疾病患者（如肺气肿、肺心病等病人）；精神病患者（如癫痫及精神病人）；严重贫血病患者；大中型手术的恢复期病患者，孕妇及行动不便者，其他不适合