-size:12px;text-align:center;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;outline:none !important;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1px;padding:0px;margin:0px;vertical-align:middle;max-width:100%;\" /></span></span> \n		</p>\n		<div style=\"white-space:normal;background-color:#F6F5F5;color:#666666;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;text-align:center;\">\n			<span style=\"color:#333333;\"> \n			<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\n				<br />\n说起丹巴，很多小伙伴纷纷表示醉倒，想去，路不好，又太远，但是未尝晓得成都附近也有个“小丹巴”，而且可以观银杏、访古村，是一颗遗落山间的明珠，风景不比丹巴差！<br />\n			</div>\n</span> \n		</div>\n		<div style=\"white-space:normal;background-color:#F6F5F5;color:#666666;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;\">\n		</div>\n<span style=\"white-space:normal;background-color:#F6F5F5;color:#666666;font-family:微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;outline-color:initial !important;outline-width:initial !important;\"><img src=\"/web/kindeditor/attached/image/20171116/20171116123601_57345.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:middle;max-width:100%;outline:none !important;\" /></span></span><span style=\"white-space:normal;background-color:#F6F5F5;\"></span> \n		<p class=\"empty\" style=\"white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;text-align:center;outline:none !important;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1px;padding:0px 0px 1px;\">\n			<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;\"><br />\n小丹巴它就位于崇州市文锦江镇大坪村，</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;\">与鸡冠山、街子古镇、九龙沟相邻。</span> \n		</p>\n		<div style=\"white-space:normal;background-color:#F6F5F5;color:#666666;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;text-align:center;\">\n			<span style=\"color:#333333;\"><br />\n</span> \n		</div>\n<span style=\"white-space:normal;background-color:#F6F5F5;color:#666666;font-family:微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;outline-color:initial !important;outline-width:initial !important;\"><img src=\"/web/kindeditor/attached/image/20171116/20171116123611_17973.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:middle;max-width:100%;outline:none !important;\" /></span></span><span style=\"white-space:normal;background-color:#F6F5F5;\"></span> \n		<p style=\"white-space:normal;background-color:#F6F5F5;color:#666666;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;\">\n			<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"><br />\n同丹巴一样，以山地为主，林木葱茏，云雾多，日照少。是遗落在深山里的自然生态之美，美到美爆！</span> \n		</p>\n		<p class=\"empty\" style=\"white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;text-align:center;outline:none !important;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1px;padding:0px 0px 1px;\">\n			<br />\n<img src=\"/web/kindeditor/attached/image/20171116/20171116123623_43939.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"850\" height=\"566\" title=\"\" align=\"\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:middle;max-width:100%;outline:none !important;\" /> \n		</p>\n		<p class=\"empty\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:1px;white-space:normal;background-color:#F6F5F5;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0px 0px 1px;\">\n			<br />\n		</p>\n		<div style=\"white-space:normal;background-color:#F6F5F5;\">\n		</div>\n<span style=\"white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;text-align:center;outline:none !important;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;\">这里春夏秋冬各有特色，现在是初冬季节，银杏黄，漆树红，满山赤橙黄绿甚是好看，再加上村子的衬托，完全就是“村在林中，林在村中”的画卷！</span></span><span style=\"white-space:normal;background-color:#F6F5F5;\"></span><br style=\"white-space:normal;background-color:#F6F5F5;\" />\n<span style=\"white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;text-align: