ify;white-space:normal;widows:1;\">&nbsp;耿达镇，距都江堰不足40公里，地处国家级卧龙自然保护区境内，是世界自然遗产大熊猫栖息地的腹心区域，这里气候宜人，风景如画，是最适宜人类居住的海拔高度1500米，负氧离子爆表，空气清新指数满格。</span></span> \n</p>\n<img src=\"/web/kindeditor/attached/image/20171201/20171201161508_14587.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n<p>\n	<img src=\"/web/kindeditor/attached/image/20171201/20171201161527_39717.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-left:21.0000pt;text-indent:-21.0000pt;text-align:justify;background:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:&quot;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;color:#333333;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;\">熊猫坪位于四川卧龙镇耿达乡，</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:&quot;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;color:#333333;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;\">当地人称之为牛坪（因为山上有很多牛），我们称它为熊猫坪，在它的山脚下就是全球最大卧龙熊猫基地。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;text-align:justify;background:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span></span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;text-align:justify;background:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span><img src=\"/web/kindeditor/attached/image/20171201/20171201161534_67715.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;text-align:justify;background:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span><img src=\"/web/kindeditor/attached/image/20171201/20171201161543_86048.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<img src=\"/web/kindeditor/attached/image/20171201/20171201161554_34687.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n<p>\n	<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;line-height:25.6px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;widows:1;\">这里有红松林，喇嘛庙，密密的灌木丛，高山流水，冬日皑皑白雪，夏季遍地野花</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333;\">...</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<img src=\"/web/kindeditor/attached/image/20171201/20171201161618_83748.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/web/kindeditor/attached/image/20171201/20171201161630_96351.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/web/kindeditor/attached/image/20171201/20171201161643_55965.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/web/kindeditor/attached/image/20171201/20171201161653_33137.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/web/kindeditor/attached/image/20171201/20171201161701_95808.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21pt;text-indent:-21pt;\">\n	<span style=\"color:#333333;font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"color:#919191;font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;line-height:25.6px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;widows:1;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;font-size:14px;\">耿达镇――守护大熊猫的古老藏族民俗镇。千万年来，这里的藏族同胞和羌族、回族、汉族同胞一起，世代在这 块土地上辛勤劳作，繁衍生息。他们保存着传统的民风民俗，忠诚地守护着我们大熊猫和我们的家园！</span><br />\n</span></span> \n</p>\n<div id=\"ydxz\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;border-width:1px 1px 3px;border-style:solid;border-color:#DCDCDC #DCDCDC #FF8800;border-image:initial;vertical-align:baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;font-family:微软雅黑;height:40px;line-height:40px;background:#F6F5F5;position:relative;color:#666666;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;\">\n	<h2 class=\"detailh2\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px 20px;font-size:14px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;float:left;display:inline;color:#4F4F4F;\">\n		<img style=\"height:20px;vertical-align:middle;\" src=\"/web/tubiao/5.png\" /><span class=\"icon-bright\" style=\"margin:0px 10px 0px 0px;padding:0px;border:0px;vertical-align:middle;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;background-image:url(\" background-repeat:no-repeat;display:inline-block;width:16px;height:16px;background-position:-217px=\"\" -80px;\"=\"\"> </span><span>预订须知</span> \n	</h2>\n</div>\n<div style=\"margin:0px 0px 15px;padding:0px 0px 6px;border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:solid;border-color:#DCDCDC;border-image:initial;vertical-align:baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;font-family:微软雅黑;background:#F6F5F5;font-size:14px;color:#666666;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;\">\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:10px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;\">\n		<div style=\"color:#666666;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;background-color:#F6F5F5;outline:none !important;\">\n			<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-weight:700;color:#333333;outline:none !important;\">【费用须知】</span> \n		</div>\n		<div style=\"color:#666666;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;background-color:#F6F5F5;outline:none !important;\">\n			<span style=\"color:#333333;\">费用包含：</span>1、全程往返大巴费用。<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2、户外徒步保险费。<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;3、专业户外领队。<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;4<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">、</span>组织成本费及各项杂费。\n		</div>\n		<div style=\"color:#666666;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;background-color:#F6F5F5;outline:none !important;\">\n			<div>\n				<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;outline:none !important;\">费用不含</span><span style=\"color:#333333;\">：</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">1、</span>全程餐饮费用。<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">2、其他个人消费。</span> \n			</div>\n<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\"> \n			<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">\n				<div>\n					<b><br />\n</b> \n				</div>\n<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-weight:700;outline:none !important;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;\">【报名须知】</span></span> \n			</div>\n			<div>\n				<span style=\"color:#333333;\">在线报名：</span>活动页面“选择批次”，然后点击“立即报名”进行网上报名，按照要求提交有效信息。<br />\n			</div>\n			<div>\n				<span style=\"color:#333333;\">退费须知：</span>成功报名后不支持退款，如需退款在活动<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">前</span>36小时找客服申请退款，36小时内因个人原因退出不予退费。<br />\n			</div>\n			<div>\n				<span style=\"color:#333333;\">客服微信：</span><span style=\"color:#FF9900;\">tunaer-club</span><br />\n			</div>\n			<div>\n				<span style=\"color:#333333;\">客服电话：</span><span style=\"color:#FF9900;\">13540139792</span><br />\n			</div>\n			<div>\n				<span style=\"color:#333333;\">QQ群：</span><span style=\"color:#FF9900;\">256606057</span><br />\n			</div>\n			<div>\n				<span style=\"color:#333333;\">徒哪儿微信公众号：</span><span style=\"color:#FF9900;\">cdtunaer</span> \n			</div>\n<br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\" />\n			<div>\n				<span style=\"font-weight:700;color:#333333;\">以下人员请勿报名:</span> \n			</div>\n<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">参加活动的人员须身体健康，户外活动可能对身体和精神方面都有严格的要求，可能远离救助和医疗服务，凡隐瞒自己疾病，给团队和个人造成损失者，一切后果自付，并负相应法律责任。(1)传染性疾病患者，如传染性肝炎、活动期肺结核、伤寒等传染病人;(2)心血管疾病患者，如严重高血压、心功能不全、心肌缺氧、心肌梗塞等病人;(3)脑血管疾病患者，如脑栓塞、脑出血、脑肿瘤等病人;(4)呼吸系统疾病患者，如肺气肿、肺心病等病人;(5)精神病患者，如癫痫及各种精神病人;(6)严重贫血病患者，如血红蛋白量水平在50克/升以下的病人;(7)大中型手术的恢复期病患者;(8)孕妇及行动不便者;(9)其他不适合出去旅行的疾病。</span></span> \n		</div>\n	</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"qtxx\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;border-width:1px 1px 3px;border-style:solid;border-color:#DCDCDC #DCDCDC #FF8800;border-image:initial;vertical-align:baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;font-family:微软雅黑;height:40px;line-height:40px;background:#F6F5F5;position:relative;color:#666666;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;\">\n	<h2 class=\"detailh2\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px 20px;font-size:14px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;float:left;display:inline;color:#4F4F4F;\">\n		<img style=\"height:20px;vertical-align:middle;\" src=\"/web/tubiao/3.png\" /><span class=\"icon-bright\" style=\"margin:0px 10px 0px 0px;padding:0px;border:0px;vertical-align:middle;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;background-image:url(\" background-repeat:no-repeat;display:inline-block;width:16px;height:16px;background-position:-217px=\"\" -80px;\"=\"\"> </span><span>其他信息</span> \n	</h2>\n</div>\n<div style=\"margin:0px 0px 15px;padding:0px 0px 6px;border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:solid;border-color:#DCDCDC;border-image:initial;vertical-align:baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;font-family:微软雅黑;background:#F6F5F5;font-size:14px;color:#666666;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;\">\n	<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:10px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;\">\n		<div style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;background-color:#F6F5F5;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">\n			<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">\n				<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:18pt;outline:none !important;\"> \n				<div>\n					<span style=\"font-weight:700;text-indent:18pt;\"><span style=\"color:#666666;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;\">【活动声明】</span></span><span style=\"color:#E53333;\"><br />\n</span></span><span style=\"color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">我们是一群喜欢户外运动的</span><span style=\"color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">AA</span><span style=\"color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">制徒友，所有领队有义务保护好大家安全、同时也希望大家听从领队的安排。</span><span style=\"color:#E53333;text-indent:18pt;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\"><span style=\"color:#666666;\">徒步不等同于旅游。徒友们在参加活动的过程过中，应遵循徒哪儿网活动规则。<br />\n</span></span><span style=\"color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;\">一、安全第一；上车请系好安全带，徒步中遇见危险地段请呼叫领队，</span> \n				</div>\n				<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">\n					<span style=\"color:#666666;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:18pt;outline:none !important;\"> \n					<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:0px;outline:none !important;\">\n						<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:18pt;outline:none !important;\">二、徒友们不争吵，不在微信群里语言重伤他人。</span> \n					</div>\n</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:18pt;outline:none !important;\"> \n					<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:0px;outline:none !important;\">\n						<div style=\"color:#E53333;\">\n							<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;outline:none !important;\">三、参加活动的徒友们请按时遵守集合时间；超出规定时间可以等待</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;outline:none !important;\">5</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;outline:none !important;\">分钟，如特殊情况最多等待</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;outline:none !important;\">10</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;outline:none !important;\">分钟将发车，反程同</span><span style=\"color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;\">样遵守时间，没有赶上车的徒友将不在退款。</span> \n						</div>\n<span style=\"text-indent:18pt;\"> \n						<div style=\"text-indent:0px;\">\n							<span style=\"color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;\">四、请徒友们严格按照分车信息（车牌号、车辆编号）上车。<br />\n</span><span style=\"color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;\">五、不准在车上吃东西，吃东西请提前在车下吃好，以免车上气味过大。<br />\n</span><span style=\"color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;\">六、不准在临近发车时上厕所。<br />\n</span><span style=\"color:#666666;text-indent:18pt;\">七、徒友回城上车请原车原位就坐，不得调换车位及车辆。<br />\n</span><span style=\"text-indent:18pt;\"><span style=\"color:#666666;\">八、爱护环境，不乱扔垃圾，不破坏植物，养成好的习惯，鼓励拾捡垃圾。做到“只留下你的脚印，只带走你的回忆”。<br />\n九、徒步的过程中养成看路标的习惯，特别是遇到岔路口时，应多看，视觉看远一点。<br />\n十、徒步应备好基本的徒步装备，登山鞋，登山杖，登山背包。<br />\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent:18pt;color:#E53333;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">十一、</span><span style=\"text-indent:18pt;color:#E53333;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">小孩报名参加活动同样占车位，不能由大人抱着</span><span style=\"text-indent:18pt;color:#E53333;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">。</span> \n						</div>\n</span> \n					</div>\n</span> \n				</div>\n<br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\" />\n</span> \n			</div>\n		</div>\n		<div style=\"font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;color:#333333;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;background-color:#F6F5F5;font-family:&quot;outline:none !important;\">\n			<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;font-weight:700;outline:none !important;\">【请徒友们注意】</span> \n		</div>\n<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;color:#666666;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:center;background-color:#F6F5F5;outline:none !important;\"> \n		<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:left;outline:none !important;\">\n			<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">1、由于户外活动具有一定的风险，可能对身体素质和精神状态方面有一定的要求，可能远离救助和医疗服务。请参与者仔细阅读、谨慎报名，如报名成功、对报名者均视为有完全民事责任。故患有：传染性疾病(如传染性肝炎、活动期肺炎、伤寒等）；心血管疾病（如严重高血压、心功能不全、心肌缺氧、心肌梗塞等病人），脑血管疾病患者（如脑栓塞、脑出血、脑肿瘤等病人）；呼吸系统疾病患者（如肺气肿、肺心病等病人）；精神病患者（如癫痫及精神病人）；严重贫血病患者；大中型手术的恢复期病患者，孕妇及行动不便者，其他不适合出去旅行的疾病等。参加活动的人员必须身体健康。凡隐瞒自己疾病，给团队和个人造成损失者，一切后果由其全权负责。</span> \n		</div>\n</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;color:#666666;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:center;background-color:#F6F5F5;outline:none !important;\"> \n		<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:left;outline:none !important;\">\n			<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">2、活动参与所有人员，均统一购买户外10万高风险意外保险，为保障安全，严禁无保险的人员随车参加活动。</span> \n		</div>\n</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;color:#666666;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:center;background-color:#F6F5F5;outline:none !important;\"> \n		<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:left;outline:none !important;\">\n			<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">3、根据客运管理规定，严格一人一座（含小孩），严禁超载带来安全隐患,请各位家长自觉遵守规定。</span> \n		</div>\n</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;color:#666666;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:center;background-color:#F6F5F5;outline:none !important;\"> \n		<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:left;outline:none !important;\">\n			<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">4、为避免户外风险，切实保障徒友的安全，活动年龄限制为<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#E53333;outline:none !important;\">5岁~65岁</span>，15岁以下孩子（本次活动年龄下限5岁 ）必须由监护人陪同才能报名参加活动。65岁以上个人员必须有领队批准，有同行人员陪同方可报名。由此给大家带来的不便，请大家谅解！</span> \n		</div>\n</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;color:#666666;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:center;background-color:#F6F5F5;outline:none !important;\"> \n		<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:left;outline:none !important;\">\n			<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">5、严禁携带任何宠物参加活动，违者领队将有权取消活动资格。</span> \n		</div>\n</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;color:#666666;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:center;background-color:#F6F5F5;outline:none !important;\"> \n		<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:left;outline:none !important;\">\n			<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">6、本活动为自助式户外徒步活动，属于自发组织的休闲锻炼性质，不是旅游，没有导游，因此无法向参与者提供任何个性化的商业服务！</span> \n		</div>\n</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;color:#666666;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:center;background-color:#F6F5F5;outline:none !important;\"> \n		<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:left;outline:none !important;\">\n			<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">7、参加活动务必听从领队的安排及安全劝导，坚决杜绝个人主义，一定携带必要的安全装备，不得做任何无安全保障的户外行为！</span> \n		</div>\n</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;color:#666666;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:center;background-color:#F6F5F5;outline:none !important;\"> \n		<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:left;outline:none !important;\">\n			<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">8、为保证活动安全，严禁利用他人身份证报名参加活动（会出现无户外保险，超龄及有相关不适合参与户外活动疾病的人员，对本人，家庭，及活动会产生极大的安全隐患！），违者将自行承担一切后果。</span> \n		</div>\n</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;color:#666666;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:center;background-color:#F6F5F5;outline:none !important;\"> \n		<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:left;outline:none !important;\">\n			<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">9、 如出现冒名顶替的情况，所有安全责任由其本人及转让人承担，领队有劝导其退出活动的权利，对转让人及顶替人领队直接拉黑取消终生报名资格。</span> \n		</div>\n</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;color:#666666;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:center;background-color:#F6F5F5;outline:none !important;\"> \n		<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:left;outline:none !important;\">\n			<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">10、 报名成功后 请关注微信公众号：徒哪儿户外俱乐部 第一时间查收发出的分车信息及活动注意事项。</span> \n		</div>\n</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;color:#666666;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:center;background-color:#F6F5F5;outline:none !important;\"> \n		<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:left;outline:none !important;\">\n			<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">11、 活动出发前请务必谨记领队给出的集合时间（如出发集合时间、自由活动集合时间、返程集合时间）同去同归，不接受任何理由的迟到或早退。</span> \n		</div>\n</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;color:#666666;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:center;background-color:#F6F5F5;outline:none !important;\"> \n		<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:left;outline:none !important;\">\n			<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">12、 上车前请一定认清车牌号再上车。</span> \n		</div>\n</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;color:#666666;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:center;background-color:#F6F5F5;outline:none !important;\"> \n		<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:left;outline:none !important;\">\n			<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">13、 本次户外活动有不可预见的意外受伤（如跌倒、摔伤、中暑、迷路等），我们会尽力为大家提供就近医疗，但报名者应对自己的身体情况和本次活动的路线及危险程度有清楚的认识和了解；本俱乐部代每个队员投保十万元的户外意外保险；当事故发生时，保险公司将按不同事故的理赔标准给予赔负；本俱乐部不承当另外任何责任；但本俱乐部将尽一切努力进行救护和援助。</span> \n		</div>\n</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;color:#666666;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:center;background-color:#F6F5F5;outline:none !important;\"> \n		<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:left;outline:none !important;\">\n			<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">14、 领队有权因天气情况或者不可抗拒因素进行、行程的适当调整、参与人员须服从领队的安排；如个人不遵守活动规定和领队的指挥，或活动场地的安全规定，地方习俗、自行其事而造成的后果，除自负其责之外，还应对因此给他人造成的损失负责。</span> \n		</div>\n</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;color:#666666;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:center;background-color:#F6F5F5;outline:none !important;\"> \n		<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:left;outline:none !important;\">\n			<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">15、报名后，因个人因素（时间、天气、身体状况等原因），不能到达集合地点，活动费用不予退还。</span> \n		</div>\n</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;color:#666666;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:center;background-color:#F6F5F5;outline:none !important;\"> \n		<div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:left;outline:none !important;\">\n			<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:none !important;\">16、活动期间，因个人原因（时间、天气、身体状况、个人体能等原因）不能到达预定目的地，活动费用不予退还。</span> \n		</div>\n</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.5px;white-space:normal;color:#666666;box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:center;backgro