nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>加榜梯田</a></span></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">▲清晨推开窗门，云雾袅绕，一阵仙气袭来。<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;行摄于绿野仙踪之间，仿佛置身世外。<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;恍惚之际，只见这抹白烟悄悄地蔓延，笼罩着小村寨。<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;鸡鸣、鸟啼以及远处的吆喝声，此起彼伏，<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;小村寨的人们，开始苏醒了……</p><div id=\"_j_photo_229663578\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/CE/CE/wKgBZ1l9rEKAbQQuACDc36j2tVg04.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 507px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px; padding-left: 0px;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"_j_anchor\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin