; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>小黄侗寨</a></span></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">▲山路十八弯，每一弯都像跌进了宫崎骏的童话世界中。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_229663582\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/CE/DD/wKgBZ1l9rE6ATJL1AB7NdVqyTIk93.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 507px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px; padding-left: 0px;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"_j_anchor\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>西江千户苗寨</a></span></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">▲午后的风雨桥上，微风依然，人们怡然自得。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_229663581\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/CE/D8/wKgBZ1l9rEuAZtybABj49Dzn9oU11.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 507px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px; padding-left: 0px;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"_j_anchor\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>堂安侗寨</a></span></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">▲从<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">肇兴</a>到<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">堂安</a>，海拔垂直上升500米，满眼的梯田风光。<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;在这里，徒步也是一种不错的选择。</p><div id=\"_j_paragraph_1\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><h2 class=\"t6\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 22px; height: 86px; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/t6.gif&quot;) 0px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-weight: normal; text-align: center;\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 95px; display: block; margin: 0px 120px 0px 70px;\">我们的线路与行程</span></h2></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;对于这个行程嘛，给我的感觉就是从不食人间烟火的仙境，慢慢回到凡间。越往后走，去的地方越来越商业化，人越来越多，玩的东西也越来越没意思。不过一趟旅程，也不能完全避开旅行社扎堆的景点吧。<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">比如</a><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">西江</a>千户苗寨，虽然深知商业化严重，但还是不甘心，非要凑热闹过去看一眼，看看为何能吸引如此多的游客。事实上，未被开发的景区有它独有的宁静，而开发完善的地方也有它不可取代的魅力。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_229657152\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/CA/D5/wKgBZ1l9qD6AXWEgAAQ0wc2vvPc83.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 585px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">【行程概览】<br/>第1天：<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">广州</a>-<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">贵阳</a>-<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">荔波</a>县城<br/>第2天：大七孔-小七孔-樟江夜市<br/>第3天：<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">荔波</a>县城-加榜梯田<br/>第4天：高增侗寨--<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">小黄侗寨</a>--<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">肇兴</a>侗寨<br/>第5天：<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">堂安</a>侗寨--<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">镇远</a>古城<br/>第6天：高过河漂流-<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">西江</a>千户苗寨<br/>第7天：<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">青岩古镇</a>—<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">贵阳</a>北</p><div id=\"_j_paragraph_2\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><h2 class=\"t6\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 22px; height: 86px; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/t6.gif&quot;) 0px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-weight: normal; text-align: center;\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 95px; display: block; margin: 0px 120px 0px 70px;\">荔波：美景是次要，美食才是重点！</span></h2></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;从<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">贵阳</a>北飞车到<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">荔波</a>县城，将近300公里，直到下午5点我们才到达客栈。奔波了一天的我们，直接躺下就睡着了。晚上7点，当我们走到附近的樟江夜市时，天依然很亮，夜市才刚刚开始热闹。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_229260401\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B4/D6/wKgBZ1l8CjeAGy43AAvNvicFNlA79.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px; padding-left: 0px;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>荔波</a></span></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">一、豆花烤鱼<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;这里几乎每一家都是吃豆花烤鱼的，鱼鲜少刺，豆花嫩滑，配上各种特调配料，竟然毫无违和感。虽说我是从小吃甜的豆花长大的，但这又辣又咸的豆花依然能吸引我的味蕾，让我久久不能忘怀。<br/></p><div id=\"_j_photo_229260403\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://a2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B4/EC/wKgBZ1l8CmaAD6pbAAiOhU9kYSE68.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px; padding-left: 0px;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>荔波</a></span></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">二、香猪肉<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;我们还点了听起来很出名的香猪肉，这就差强人意了。肉硬，难嚼，对比起我们<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">广东</a>人吃的任何一道猪肉的菜式都要差。完全没有我们大<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">广东</a>烧排骨、猪颈肉等菜式的精髓，不好吃不好吃。后来我们在<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">从江</a>那边又尝了一次香猪肉，依然不好吃。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_229260402\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B4/E1/wKgBZ1l8Ck-AchWEAAipuVH3vGE45.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px; padding-left: 0px;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>荔波</a></span></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">三、各种酒<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;在这边，有各种自酿的酒。老板很热情地拿了几种酒给我们试，分别是桃花酒、青梅酒、酸梅酒、杨梅酒，度数都很低，一般女生都可以尝一点，10元/杯。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_229281018\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/C4/AB/wKgBZ1l8IPmAVL-vAAurhOEdWm868.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px; padding-left: 0px;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>荔波</a></span></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">四、酸梅汁<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;话说我也行走江湖多年了，喝了很多地方的酸梅汁。而这里的酸梅汁，真的很一般。感觉就是兑水的，不是原汁原味的酸梅，口感太塑料了。5元中杯，7元大杯，反正我一杯都不想喝完。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_229260400\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B4/C0/wKgBZ1l8CiqAIRw-AAWD3y1fhKY23.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px; padding-left: 0px;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>荔波</a></span></div><div id=\"_j_photo_229260404\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://a2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B4/F9/wKgBZ1l8CnyAH128AAtqEAFTzZQ99.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px; padding-left: 0px;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>荔波</a></span></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;吃饱喝足睡够，就开始我们的行程咯！说起<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">荔波</a>，大家都知道小七孔。自从《跟着贝尔去冒险》在这里拍摄过之后，小七孔景区更是火爆，那座桥也成为大家必定合影留念的标志性建筑。我最怕人多且火爆的景区，所以在大家都挤破头皮去小七孔的时候，我们先玩了大七孔。<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;在此之前，我看了许多大七孔与小七孔的攻略，说各有特色，都值得玩。通过我的亲身游玩，再加上两者门票几乎相差一半的价格来看，我觉得只玩小七孔一个景点就足够了。小七孔里面的景点有很多，像我这种喜欢在原生态的地方徒步，而且又爱停下来拍照的人，用一天时间好好地玩小七孔真的非常有意思。备好干粮，早点出发避开人群，静静地潜进去玩，肯定会有意外收获的。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_229260405\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://a1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B5/06/wKgBZ1l8CpCAXJgaAAkgd7bk4TA10.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px; padding-left: 0px;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"_j_anchor\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>大七孔景区</a></span></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">▲景区在重新规划，不管是去大七孔还是小七孔，都在同一个地方购票。随后坐相应的观光车前往景区即可。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_229281020\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://c3-q.mafengwo.net