-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 525px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/E5/77/wKgBZ1mFifCAVX_2AADN4KL0Fsg49.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 564px; width: 525px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px; padding-left: 0px;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"_j_anchor\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>丽江四方街</a></span></div><div id=\"_j_photo_231655910\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 500px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/E5/78/wKgBZ1mFifCAVlxUAAHTu0ZoWks77.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 526px; width: 500px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px; padding-left: 0px;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"_j_anchor\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>丽江四方街</a></span></div><div id=\"_j_paragraph_3\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><h2 class=\"t1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 22px; height: 86px; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/t1.gif&quot;) 0px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-weight: normal;\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 95px; display: block;\">景洪，锦虹</span></h2></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">澜沧江</a>流经的<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">西双版纳</a>，是彩云之南久负盛名的旅游地，也是<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">云南</a>最早开发的国内热门旅游目的地。<br/>旅行，其实是很私人的事情，看世界就是看人文，看自然。<br/>在国外我喜欢看世界文化遗产，毕竟世界文化遗产是由联合国发起、联合国教育科学文化组织执行的国际公约建制，目的是保存对全世界人类都具有杰出普遍性价值的自然或文化处所为，所以世界文化遗产是文化的保护与传承的最高等级。我们<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">中国</a>今年共有52个，比<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">意大利</a>少一个，位列全球第二。<br/>在国内，我建议去一个地方首选5A景点，就像看病首选三甲，毕竟它代表一个省及全国景点的最高水平。国家旅游局评定的5A景区，就是一个金字招牌，谁拥有就能有更多的境内外客源市场份额。<br/><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">西双版纳</a>5A景点只有一个——中科院热带植物园。门票价格公道，植物园面积非常大，仔细看需要走一天时间，首推。<br/>我把对这些景区的个人看法写出来，给大家参考一下。<br/>1&nbsp;中科院热带植物园，5A景区，非常推荐。<br/>版纳热带雨林景观最具代表性也是最大的一个景区。有东区和西区，西区是一个岛，人工规划的植物园，坐电瓶车游览需要半小时左右。如果对植物感兴趣，一定会喜欢这里。东区是原始热带雨林，可以坐电瓶车到东区入口（东区到西区坐电瓶车都要20分钟时间），东区有一些小山，需要自己走上去，沿路有热带雨林植物景观，有一个景点叫美猴岩，还能看到一些猴子，不过是圈养的。<br/>2&nbsp;原始森林公园，4A景区。<br/>如果去了中科院热带植物园，其他的热带雨林为主的景区都可不必去。因为<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">大同</a>小异。这个公园的特点是有一个湖，每天有孔雀放飞表演，值得一看。而且离<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">景洪</a>市区比较近，交通方便。时间多的玩家可以考虑。<br/>3&nbsp;基诺山寨，4A景区。<br/>主要展示基诺族的传统文化的，但是景区门票160，还没有学生票。游客要跟着带队导游进去，看看表演，卖卖茶叶，一个多小时就出来了。这个地方因为上过央视的节目开始被人们知晓，但是很商业化，也是人为因素多一些，个人觉得没意思。<br/>4&nbsp;热带雨林谷，3A景区。<br/>比较坑，门票贵，基本上参团旅行社的导游带队进去，旅行社联合合作的人为景区，有个克木人村寨，景区很小，表演也没意思。去过望天树和中科院植物园，这个大可不必去。<br/>5&nbsp;望天树，4A景区。<br/>这个景区还可以，游览需要2小时，但是距离<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">景洪</a>市很远，坐车单程都要两个多小时。最大的看点是空中树冠走廊，和世界上最高的乔木之一——望天树。【爸爸去哪儿】刘烨儿子晚上遇见野象那期应该就去了这里，门票套票198.<br/>6.勐泐大佛寺是宣传最多的，建在山上，金碧辉煌，如果去最好在网上订票。我在门口买票120，后来才知道，网上订票只要三四十。。。这个寺庙除了修建的气派，里面其实一个僧人都没有，纯粹供游客参观的。要去有点历史底蕴的，建议去总佛寺，这个是货真价实的寺庙，很多<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">东南亚</a>的游团都会来此参观。可以从总佛寺直通曼听公园，从总佛寺后门进入曼听公园不要门票。勐泐大佛看似恢弘大气，实际上是近期的<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">新建</a>筑，在山上俯瞰风景还不错。<br/>7.野象谷，交通不便，可以骑大象，但是很难看到野象，而且我个人很不喜欢这些驯养动物的商业，不推荐；<br/>8.橄榄坝傣族园，个人觉得不错，交通方便，景区也很大。单买门票一个人50，如果看表演和泼水，应该就要180。这里是最早开发做旅游的村寨，位于<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">景洪</a>东南约30公里处的<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">勐罕</a>镇，几百户傣族人家世世代代在这里生活，所以这里具有当地浓郁热带风光和民族色彩，这里热带水果种类繁多，除鲜果外，还出产大量的果脯，手工艺品。里面有两个比较大的寨子，一个是曼松满，也就是花园寨，另一个是曼听，也就是花果寨，无论你走进哪一个寨子，都会看到典型的缅寺佛塔和传统的傣家竹楼。现在很多都做了民宿农家乐，傣族人很爱干净，所以卫生情况我不是特别担心。这里每天下午3点都会有表演，之后在广场上有大型的泼水活动，游客可以参加。【爸爸去哪儿】也在这里拍摄过。<br/>9.再次，市区的一些佛寺和公园值得看看：<br/>热带花卉植物园，门票是20还是40我记不清了，下午五六点后免费。里面植物造景还不错，对植物花草感兴趣值得去看看。我喜欢拍照喜欢花，所以头一个选择就是这个景区。<br/>10.南药园，几乎是个荒废的公园，游客少，免门票，不值得去。<br/>主要景区就是这些，首推中科院热带植物园，其他景点凭个人喜欢，看自然风景，花卉植物，还是文化宗教来选择吧。<br/><br/>我选择<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">自驾</a>的原因就是时间自由，可以走走停停。再一次回味了当年逛过的中科院植物园，热带花卉公园，橄榄坝傣家寨，把民族风情，热带雨林都感受了一遍，也在心底重温了那段时光，满脸稚气扎着羊角辫的女孩，有着唇边毛绒胡渣身上带着小兔子味道的男孩，从相遇相知到别离。<br/><br/>每张旧照片都有阳光的味道，那时的你我青涩而甜蜜，仿佛身上有彩虹锦绣，谁曾想，人群里的一眼竟是终身。<br/><br/>在橄榄坝，我耳畔回荡着妈妈最爱的曲子《月光下的凤尾竹》，想起傣族民间传说很久以前，山洪爆发中一位傣家小卜冒抱起一个大葫芦，闯过惊涛骇浪，救出自己的心上人，他忠贞不渝的爱情感动了佛祖，佛祖给葫芦装上了管子，小卜冒吹出了美妙的乐声，顿时风平浪静，鲜花盛开，孔雀开屏，祝愿这对情侣吉祥幸福。从此葫芦丝在傣族人家世代相传。虽然这被传颂的故事只是神话，它仍然充分表达了人们对情比金坚的赞誉和向往。这是人类最本性最内在的需求，人类就靠着这无形的信念支撑着生命繁衍生息。<br/>那年看到原始森林里表演的大象，我质疑活着是被奴役，尊严来自哪里？<br/>我问你，为什么我们有那么多欲求而不得？<br/>你告诉我，生命本就是被动的选择，所有的主动，都是在既定的答案中选择。<br/>今天我终于明白了这句话的含义。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_229359642\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F8/74/wKgBZ1l8VruAFnbVAAv0W_L8qFA24.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px; padding-left: 0px;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"_j_anchor\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>曼听公园</a></span></div><div id=\"_j_photo_229359644\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F8/78/wKgBZ1l8VsCAEn0EAAk9JDfaeHQ78.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 412px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px; padding-left: 0px;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"_j_anchor\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>曼听公园</a></span></div><div id=\"_j_photo_231624734\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 138, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative; zoom: 1;\"></a></div><p><br/></p>',2,'2017-09-08 14:06:49','初秀 /自驾/一路向南，我的前半生不再见/【景洪，老挝】','1504879608.jpeg',15,0,0),(11,0,'<p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">出行前的叨叨<br/>一、轻轻松松—<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">桂林</a><br/>初识《<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">桂林</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;山水》是在小学课本中，每每想到“舟行碧波上，人在画中游“的美景，就会有想去膜拜一番的冲动。今年蠢蠢欲动的心再也抑制不住，心想祖国那么大，我怎么也得去看看——先定个小目标吧，从南向北把祖国的大好河山游览遍，那就从<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">桂林</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;山水看起吧。<br/>如果非要给此次出行写下些理由的话：为了暂时远离北方雾都城市，去自然氧吧来一场与大自然的亲密接触？为了自拍、摆拍、闺蜜拍、随性拍？总之在本身就是一幅画的地方再加上“<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">邯郸</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;三朵花”岂不更完美！当然这些原因都不是最主要的，最主要的是有假，哈哈哈！在这里我给大家推荐一下一个很好的包车师傅小赵，小赵师傅是我这次旅途的包车师傅，我把他的联系方式留下了哦，电话：18376361798（微信同号）<br/>二、轻轻松松—我们<br/>从<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">邯郸</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;到<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">桂林</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;将近两千公里，目前不考虑<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">自驾</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;游，我们纠结跟团还是自助游，想想各有利弊:<br/>&lt;跟团&gt;&nbsp;优点是省心，缺点是节奏快、机械、到景点不能深度游、固定线路无法选择心仪线路；<br/>&lt;自助&gt;&nbsp;优点是时间自由、休闲、自行选择景点、随时随地体验当地特色美食与风俗，缺点是前期功课要做足了，需要自己安排食、宿、行。<br/>对于选择恐惧症晚期患者来讲最讨厌的便是选择，讲真对于上班狗来讲出趟远门不易，且行且珍惜。我们仨合计即使报了团临时想玩了、想买了还是抵挡不住诱惑，最终银子还是会偷偷从口袋里溜走。为了玩的开心、拍的尽兴，SO选择自助游。<br/>自由行最繁琐的就是提前做功课，不过乐趣也多多呦，身为大姐大又不怕麻烦的我就光荣的担任起了这次自助游的总策划师。<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">桂林</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;虽不像<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">云南</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;景点那样分散，但是考虑到仅仅只有5天的行程，为了玩的更加尽兴，结合之前各位大侠给出的攻略，我觉得选择在当地包车不错，于是就在某宝上选了家性价比不错的店拍了下来。<br/>三、轻轻松松—机场篇<br/>3月31日是一个阳光明媚的日纸，黄历显示宜出行，于是乎我、佩佩、萌妹“闺蜜团“就此粗发了。从<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">邯郸</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;到<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">桂林</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;没有直飞的航班，因此我们<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">自驾</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;先抵达<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">郑州</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;，把车安顿好后，就去换登机牌，拿到牌牌后还有点小激动，期待已久的闺蜜游马上实现了。我拿出ipad开始查阅哪哪好玩，再看看这俩一个追某凯的剧，一个在疯狂的搜寻当地美食（小吃货），也是没sei了。看了一些小伙伴们分享的游记，<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">桂林</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;美景数不胜数啊，心想要不要也啰嗦一篇若干年后，三个闺蜜一起坐在夕阳下牛逼闪闪的细数我们走过的地方。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/53/8D/wKgBZ1jl4U6AEJCCAAXERUUikso12.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 604px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">新郑</a>国际机场&nbsp;&nbsp;四、轻轻松松—玩玩玩<br/>两个小时之后安全抵达两江机场，走出机场在人头攒动的人海中，我们一眼忘到了写着我们名字的一个很大的牌子，牌子下面是一个帅气的小伙，走过去询问正是之前预定好的司机师傅小赵，赵师傅热情的向我们打招呼，逗趣道：“这么多美女，早说给你们打个折啊！”然后我说“现在也不晚啊，哈哈！”在欢笑声中赵师傅帮我们拖着行李走向停车场，跟之前说的一样，给我们安排的是辆蛮新的别克商务车，路上叽叽喳喳如我们，边感受当地湿润气候边吐槽北方雾霾，差不多一小时到达市区。<br/><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">桂林</a>米粉<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/4D/5E/wKgBZ1jl2b-AXhznAAYX8MtBcfI11.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 385px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/4D/75/wKgBZ1jl2dqAfbMSAAbvTaYXbTA34.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 357px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">接下来就是这次闺蜜行的“景点玩玩玩“了！以下是我们的行程轨迹和全程的花费哦！<br/>轻轻松松—行程<br/><br/>Day1：象鼻山（门票70）—<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">靖江</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;王府独秀峰（门票110）—两江四湖（门票210）<br/><br/>Day2：遇龙河漂流(船票288两人，一个人也是288)—银子岩（门票60）—印象刘三姐（票价170）—西街<br/><br/>Day3：相公山（门票60）—世外<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">桃源</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;—十里画廊的月亮山、大榕树<br/><br/>Day4：<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">漓江</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;漂流（竹筏约98元/人，1.5小时）—兴坪古镇—<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">龙脊梯田</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;（门票95）<br/><br/>Day5：七星伴月&amp;千层天梯看日出—回程去机场<br/>D1&nbsp;象鼻山—&nbsp;<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">靖江</a>王府独秀峰—两江四湖<br/>第一站来到<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">桂林</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;市徽，小学课书上那幅图就是眼前的象鼻山，（赵师傅建议不要买门票进公园，进去后没什么看点，就是爬上象鼻山。他建议在外面买票坐竹筏，在水中看象鼻山比较好）于是乎我们坐坐竹筏体验了一番“舟行碧波上，人在画中游“的美景。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/4E/41/wKgBZ1jl2s6ATtqrAAd07nIOsfA66.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 306px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">第二站，<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">靖江</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;王府独秀峰，景区虽然不大，但规划的还不错，期间我们还跟在一个十几人的团后面听着导游详细的讲解，在展示厅里看到王府的兴衰过程，重温了下历史典故，还有小段情景剧看。贡院里的表演特别搞笑，还亲自体验了一把十年寒窗苦读一朝金榜题名。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/4E/A0/wKgBZ1jl20aASTpbACD_eF-kocU80.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 595px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/4E/E9/wKgBZ1jl25aADcD4AApLgurjvwY31.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 373px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/4E/EA/wKgBZ1jl25eAZt3KAAZIgRj55SA20.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 290px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">龙脊土鸡<br/>欣赏完一天的美景，在萌妹的软磨硬泡下，我们决定晚饭吃“龙脊土鸡“（我俩都觉得吃肉长胖，无奈萌妹这个吃货无肉不欢），据那个小吃货说这只鸡不一般，是用龙脊山泉水煮出来的土鸡，在城市是无缘享受的，价格适中，鸡肉肥嫩，味道清淡滋补，很有营养。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/4F/19/wKgBZ1jl29SAL1WIAAw-8nKHkhw70.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 597px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">吃罢晚饭，19:20司机师傅的车准时停在酒店门口，他将带我们去两江四湖。据司机师傅介绍”两江”指的是<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">漓江</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;和桃花江，”四湖”是指榕湖、木龙湖、桂湖和杉湖，是<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">桂林</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;市区最美的湖系。白天自然风光秀丽，夜游也这边风景独好，就是坐船里不好拍照，期间还有歌舞表演。乘船荡漾在熠熠发光的水面上，在五彩斑斓灯光的映射下，那桥、那树、那水、那塔显得活灵活现，醉人心玄。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/4F/41/wKgBZ1jl3BCAO09pAAlXLZ_WCMQ92.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 399px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/4F/42/wKgBZ1jl3BGAdEr1AAcB78HZCJ047.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 360px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/4F/44/wKgBZ1jl3BOATxoeAA6hh79dIOI21.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 400px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/4F/6D/wKgBZ1jl3DqAd0-EABVnm9V519464.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 446px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/4F/72/wKgBZ1jl3D2AZ8czABb2418Plp832.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 423px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/4F/73/wKgBZ1jl3ECAEtsBABCZGDVmQJ059.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 432px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">D2遇龙河漂流—银子岩—印象刘三姐—西街<br/>由于第一天的玩的比较晚，司机师傅第二天特意给我们推荐了比较轻松愉悦的项目，基本上不花体力，就是纯玩，这下满足了佩佩的小心机（来的时候就想着玩一些惊险刺激的项目），第一站漂流走起，全程只顾着享受当下了，没拍几张照片，还好萌妹留一手趁本尊不注意给抓拍了张，这次给打100分。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/4F/E1/wKgBZ1jl3MKAM5YzAAp7mAkWhys46.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 337px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/4F/E3/wKgBZ1jl3MSACf9KAA3AAeYsonc71.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 482px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/74/20/wKgBZ1kc_8CAe7DiAAHgm8yFFNg45.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 450px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/74/21/wKgBZ1kc_8CAMB86AAEoOMweQmA70.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 450px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/74/21/wKgBZ1kc_8GAElxdAAHG0QgE07026.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 799px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/74/23/wKgBZ1kc_8GAYxmFAAExXHQauLo84.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 397px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/74/24/wKgBZ1kc_8KACnX_AAE0uO6-wso06.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 450px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">老根农家饭<br/>出门旅游2件大事儿——“玩+吃“，这方”玩”罢，那方”吃”又要登场了。午饭还是萌妹精心挑选的——老根农家饭，她说：入乡就要随俗，不吃一顿地道的农家饭，就是白来一趟<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">桂林</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;。吃饭期间我们还偶遇了几个国际友人，佩佩拿出大学英语演讲级水平与之对话，实在令人佩服，不仅流利还收到了外国小朋友送的小礼物，再次论证英语的重要性啊。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/54/51/wKgBZ1jl4i6AdNjpAA_50qnMEro11.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 283px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">下午出发前，司机师傅提醒我们溶洞温度有些高，让我们穿的薄一些，可以带件厚衣服晚上逛西街时披上，不得不说南方的男人真是细心啊，还好里面穿的也漂亮，嘻嘻。<br/>到了银子岩，我们才真正领略“什么是大自然的鬼斧神工“，纯<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">卡斯</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;特地貌，自然景观美不胜收。我们一致认为：看了银子岩，别的岩洞都没什么可看了，大家随我感受一下。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/54/E4/wKgBZ1jl4sqAWMP0AAkon0oQLwY83.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 416px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/54/E5/wKgBZ1jl4syAJmBbAAj9gsVJ9-E69.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 384px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/55/40/wKgBZ1jl4xuAYFljAA2D8PcSx6I85.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 399px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">司机师傅推荐我们晚上去看“印象刘三姐“，一听说是张艺谋导演导的，佩佩坚决要去（电视、电影迷），萌妹和我对这类演出并不感冒，想着既然来了就陪她去看个热闹吧。不过确实要感谢司机师傅的推荐，也感谢佩佩的坚持。<br/>“印象刘三姐“整场演出都是山水实景演出，震撼的场景，清亮的动听弦律，除了震撼就是陶醉。山峰的隐现、水景的倒影、竹林的摇曳，这些随时都会进入演出，成为美妙的插曲。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/55/C4/wKgBZ1jl43WANGDRAByDcsOfETk76.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 393px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/55/C5/wKgBZ1jl43WAC80aAAl0lIv0UVo43.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 365px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">看完“印象刘三姐“我们来到充满异国情调的西街，都说西街是游<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">阳朔</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;必去的地方！开店的都是淳朴的<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">阳朔</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;人，他们热情、好客！街边餐馆的菜谱有中式、西式，好多外国友人在这里喝啤酒、品佳肴，名副其实的洋人街，给<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">阳朔</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;小镇增添了一道亮丽的风景线！<br/>特别提醒驴友，<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">阳朔</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;这个地方，基本上不支持支付宝，刷卡很多地方也不支持，请备好现金（幸好萌妹小吃货备足了现金）。我个人建议，从街头到街尾，吃遍所有小吃，足以当晚饭了，在西街主题就是逛吃逛吃，再加上买买买，今天就酱。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/56/77/wKgBZ1jl5CSAek1KAAm-L-ok37o74.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 333px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">D3&nbsp;相公山—世外<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">桃源</a>—十里画廊<br/>三个菇凉只差萌妹还缺一如意郎君，如果去了相公山许愿会不会立马有相公啊，哈哈，听着小赵师傅动情的介绍，萌妹说这个可以有。于是乎为了满足萌妹的小小愿望，我们赶了个大早——去给萌妹“看相公”去，因此就有了这一幕壮观的景象。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/57/19/wKgBZ1jl5MKAJ4ZdAAxXuICsO2M51.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 386px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">“初极狭，才通人，复行数十步，豁然开朗”陶渊明的这诗相信上过初中的小伙伴都不陌生。司机师傅贴心的将车停到了离景点很近的地方，一下车展现在眼前的是一片秀美的山水田园风光，穿过古老的道路小桥，乘船游览燕子湖，湖面平静，远处的山水，人家，田园，真是人间仙境啊，我们三个约定好60岁时再故地重游。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/57/44/wKgBZ1jl5PKAQVtZAAcoV2aA7BU28.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 363px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/57/45/wKgBZ1jl5POAIA_KAAoEV0hg4ZM81.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 394px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/57/46/wKgBZ1jl5PSAd7KYAAb74nTGcDk64.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 369px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/57/47/wKgBZ1jl5PSAMOsxAAa5pbmI1rk00.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 380px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/57/6F/wKgBZ1jl5SaAMdFnABfta71zym018.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 460px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">司机师傅告诉我们在<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">阳朔</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;，除了西街以及遇龙河外，就属十里画廊出名了，十里画廊的游玩方式，建议我们选择单车。路两边全是景区，图腾古道，大榕树，蝴蝶泉，聚龙潭等风景区都在这五公里的路两旁。当然各个景点都要买票。坐公交3元招手停。因此租自行车游十里画廊是最佳选择，一天20元。自行车道两边加起来，比机动车道都宽，这是我见过唯一一条自行车道比机动车道宽的公路了。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/57/9C/wKgBZ1jl5WOATh_9AA763un7x0U77.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 402px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/57/9A/wKgBZ1jl5WGAILbhAA1SdDtSVLc26.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 529px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/57/98/wKgBZ1jl5V-AEEzgAAf--5Q_6zA34.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 257px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">没错还是萌妹给拍的，哎，交友不慎啊！<br/>椿记烧鹅<br/>傍晚去久负盛名的椿记烧鹅吃东西，到了那里人还真多，需要等位，我仨不介意和别人拼一张大圆桌。烧鹅确实不错，肥而不腻，鹅皮口感香酥，鹅肉嚼起来鲜嫩有味，肉比烤鸭多汁，蘸汁更美味，总的来说还挺好，因为是节假日还免费送了果盘，不虚此行。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/58/1F/wKgBZ1jl5geAOHkfAAjIkLC5gcc06.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 388px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">D4&nbsp;<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">漓江</a>漂流—兴坪古镇—<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">龙脊梯田</a><br/><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">漓江</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;的水是清凌凌的水，<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">漓江</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;的天是蓝盈盈的天，对于一个土生土长的北方人，看到此景真是莫大的奢侈啊，平时只能当电脑桌面的美景呈现在眼前，整个人都神清气爽了。佩佩、萌妹与我边感受着大自然的美景，边大口大口呼吸着新鲜的氧气，坐着竹筏荡漾在青山碧水中，悠闲而畅快，享受当下美好，不一会到了20元人民币画面的地方了，拿出20元来了一个画面还原。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 138, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px;\"></a></p><p><br/></p>',2,'2017-09-08 14:07:45','魅力桂丽林，梦境','1504879664.jpeg',18,0,0),(12,0,'<p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">在三月，在冬季的尾巴，来到雪国。<br/>有一种宿命的感觉。<br/><br/>越是寒冷的地方，因为低温对皮肤和神经的刺激，就愈能让人精神紧绷。然而<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">北海道</a>，却并不如此。即使是徒步在大雪纷飞里，也想就这样靠着雪地躺下去，就着这绵延到一望无际的白，无人打扰的，做着美梦，睡到终老。我想，地球上最美的冬天，上帝只留给了<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">北海道</a>。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_230728380\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&