play: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_231095451\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/80/EA/wKgBZ1mDI0uAXa51ABTB2Dv5FXc88.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_231036361\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/59/5A/wKgBZ1mC7mCAao8QACZGKk3s8TE48.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_231036362\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/59/70/wKgBZ1mC7naASdUGABfQ24PieY079.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_paragraph_1\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><h2 class=\"t7\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 22px; height: 86px; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/t7.gif&quot;) 0px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-weight: normal;\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 95px; display: block; margin-right: 80px;\">交通</span></h2></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">首先说明下，现在是女票本人哟，哎呀，实在懒得再去注册个账号写游记啦，索性就来男票的账号打打酱油了。希望各位同学不要看着看着心里嘀咕：咿，怎么好像换了一个人呀？以后的游记也会是两个人用这一个账号发布，提前说明下哟。（唔，懒人癌患者就酱了）</p><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">言归正传说说交通，我们是从<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">北京</a>高铁到<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">天津</a>，然后<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">天津</a>飞到<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">函馆</a>（<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">天津</a>航空），飞猪上预定，机票含税人均970人民币往返，航班时间也都是白天。<br/><br/>如果坐标<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">北京</a>的同学可以多留意从<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">天津</a>去<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">日本</a>的机票，一般比较便宜，缺点就是落地<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">日本</a>的机场不一定是最合适你的。就好比我们这次买的是落地<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">函馆</a>机场的，其实按理说之后我们去的地方如果落地在<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">札幌</a><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">新千岁机场</a>会更合适些，不过鱼和熊掌不可兼得了。到<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">天津</a>机场check&nbsp;in的时间最好留长一些，因为票价便宜，经常有旅行团从<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">天津</a>飞往<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">日本</a>，如果碰到团，排队的时间就比较长了&nbsp;。<br/><br/>整个<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">北海道</a>的交通基本全靠JR。<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">北海道</a>只有一条从<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">函馆</a>到青森的通往省外的<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">新干</a>线，其他的区域都是没有<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">新干</a>线的，而且也基本上没有私铁，所以到哪里都是要坐JR，具体坐哪条线路下文中会具体说明。建议下了飞机就买一张<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">北海道</a>铁路周游券，指定期间内可以自由搭乘JR<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">北海道</a>线的所有列车（<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">新干</a>线除外），瞬间有种一券在手天下我有的感觉。<br/><br/>周游券分为好几种，价格也不同，可以根据实际游玩情况选择合适的券。我们买的7日券，一人24000日元，大概1400人民币，千万千万不要被这个价格吓到，其实平均算起来还是可以接受的，而且使用频次很高，如果单买的话，要贵出好几倍的价格。整个<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">北海道</a>，最贵的费用确实就是交通费，像吃饭住宿还是很平价的，整体物价水平相对于<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">东京</a>来说低很多了。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_230746445\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 610px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/92/0C/wKgBZ1mBv72AeTpjAAEuKWMCH3Y132.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 450px; width: 610px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_230746446\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/92/0D/wKgBZ1mBv76ASxpkAAKM9mfOe4c349.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 357px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_paragraph_2\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><h2 class=\"t7\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 22px; height: 86px; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/t7.gif&quot;) 0px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-weight: normal;\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 95px; display: block; margin-right: 80px;\">气候与穿衣指南</span></h2></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><br/>3月的<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">北海道</a>，室外气温大概在零下五六度，但是基本没有什么风，其实体表温度的话也就还好，不会觉得特别冷。<br/>着装参考：<br/>&gt;一件宽松的长款羽绒服和暖身宝贴&nbsp;(冬季出去玩的话你会发现这两件东西任何突发情况的时候都能用上)<br/>&gt;春秋款大衣&nbsp;毛衣&nbsp;纯色系和留白多的半身裙（在雪中纯色系衣服怎么拍照都好看呐，拍完就穿上羽绒服丝毫不会觉得冷）<br/>&gt;打底袜是一定需要的，长的厚的薄的短的可以都备一条，虽说在室外可能需要穿稍厚一点的打底袜，但如果在商场逛街，就可以像个<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">日本</a>妹子那样一双过膝袜足够了。<br/>&gt;稍厚点的围巾和贝雷帽也需要，既可以抗雪还能凹造型，要真是下雪了，谁还打伞呐，直接一条围巾一个帽子就足够了，尽情无负担的跟雪亲密接触吧；要是带了男票的话手套就可以不用带了，基本用不上而且看手机的时候超麻烦。<br/>&gt;鞋子的话，建议带一双雪地靴和一双防水性能较强的鞋子。<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">北海道</a>的雪下起来就超大超厚的，其实这样下雪的天气穿雪地靴是丝毫没压力的，但如果晴天雪开始慢慢融化的时候，就需要一双可以防水的鞋子了。<br/><br/>在<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">日本</a>大街上随处可以看到上身裹件羽绒衣下身就一条露腿短裙的妹纸们，有时候下着雪刮着风呢，依然是轻薄短裙不动声色从你身边飘过。听说<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">日本</a>上学的时候就会有一些抗寒的锻炼，可能人家练出来了，根本不怕冷，随时都可以美美的一身短裙出去逛，简直是超羡慕。</p><div id=\"_j_paragraph_3\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><h2 class=\"t7\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 22px; height: 86px; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/t7.gif&quot;) 0px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-weight: normal;\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 95px; display: block; margin-right: 80px;\">函馆➡️旭川「 踏入雪国初体验 」</span></h2></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">出<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">函馆</a>机场的时候，正好下起了大雪，本来在飞机上还不知不觉，这下子整个人就真实的进入了雪之王国。<br/>我们计划的是去程不在<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">函馆</a>停留，下了飞机直接经<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">函馆</a>去旭川，回程的时候再玩<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">函馆</a>。因为我们去的时间算是雪季的尾巴了，查了后几天的天气，北部都是在下雪，那么这几天去北部看雪是最棒的了。如果先在旭川玩几天再去北部，可能未必能赶上大雪的天气了。<br/>坐上半个小时直达JR旭川站的巴士，买好7日<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">北海道</a>铁路周游券就坐上去旭川的火车了。<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">函馆</a>离旭川的距离比较远，需要坐超级<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">北斗</a>号5个小时到<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">札幌</a>，然后在<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">札幌</a>换乘紫丁香号1个小时到旭川。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_230958063\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/26/EA/wKgBZ1mCwbGAEvVHAAjeceNoucA516.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 795px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><br/>接连几天，都住在旭川，这个<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">北海道</a>仅次于<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">札幌</a>的第二<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">大城</a>市，然而把大本营定在这里，并不是因为太想吃旭川拉面，也不是想去旭川动物园看猴子泡温泉，只是这里交通实在方便，稍微出旭川不远，聚集了许多看雪景的绝佳胜地，而且去以粉雪闻名的滑雪胜地tomamu星野度假村也是十分方便，白天可以去看绵延白雪，晚上可以回到市区吃饭和逛街，两不耽误。<br/><br/>先说说住宿，旭川真是特别善解人意的在JR站上盖了一个酒店JR&nbsp;INN，想来是知道很多人会通过旭川站中转去别的地方，而且酒店的环境非常不错，2015年开业的，设备和装修都很新，环境和服务都很不错，对一个inn来说，足够给满分了。<br/><br/>这个位于JR旭川站里的酒店,&nbsp;&nbsp;与旭川站直接相连，整体设计和设施偏无印良品风，酒店有公共泡汤区（不是温泉，是男女分开的浴场），出酒店电梯就直接连着永旺购物中心，吃饭和购物非常方便，晚九点左右购物中心的生鲜区有5折，可以下楼买几盒新鲜的刺身啊水果啊寿司啊，甚至可以连同第二天的早餐也一起买了，是不是超棒，每晚都是几盒刺生当夜宵。<br/><br/>我们3月份去的，已经进入到<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">北海道</a>的淡季了，酒店价格便宜，定的JR&nbsp;INN是400人民币一晚。虽然是在淡季的3月，依然会下很大的雪，所以对于看雪景丝毫不受影响，喜欢雪景的同学可以选择正好雪季快要结束的时候去，酒店和机票会相对便宜。agoda和booking上都可以预定，如果旺季一定要留出充足的时间提前预定，很容易满房，我刚查了一下，整个8月都满房了。<br/>贴几张官网的照片说一下酒店位置。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_230729373\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/84/E9/wKgBZ1mBrZWARYv2ABFEOoZk40A371.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 485px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">依次从左到右的建筑分别是JR旭川站、JR&nbsp;INN酒店（最高的那栋）、永旺购物中心，而且全是连通的。简直是一站式体验，省时间省力气啊。</p><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">酒店虽说装修比较简约，但空间配备感觉都是让利给客人了。快捷酒店配有书吧的并不多见，等人或者想小憩一下的时候不失为一个好去处。除了房间原本的枕头以外，酒店与枕头公司&nbsp;LOFTY&nbsp;合作开发的枕头Check&nbsp;in了之后就可以看到一个枕头区，种类很多，记忆枕乳胶枕化纤枕荞麦枕全部都有。<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">日本</a>的快捷酒店面积都不大，但足够用了，房间整洁干净，基本的配备如加湿器净化器都有，还有个可以鸟瞰的大窗户，望出去是一座大桥。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_230730053\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/84/DE/wKgBZ1mBrYKADgbwABY5qHkIxlQ427.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 482px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_230730054\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/85/0A/wKgBZ1mBrbGAbnneABbhIvZwd5U396.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 503px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_230730055\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><