e-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EA/4F/wKgBZ1mxS7yATnaTAACkletAbho42.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 399px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">　　阳光明媚，秋意盎然，今天的骑行目标是滇西名镇<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">丽江</a>。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 399px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">　　40公里的下坡大家骑得好爽！不想按下刹车，因为每个骑手都清楚，在突破点的那一端，是身心的极度愉悦在等待。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EA/4F/wKgBZ1mxS72AfF4uAAC5y4-MsoI29.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 399px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">　　经过四个小时的骑行&nbsp;到达<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">丽江</a>，稍作休整<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EA/50/wKgBZ1mxS72AQvGwAABVbWslREw36.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 399px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">　　午饭后&nbsp;慕名前去文峰寺听了银巴嘉措&nbsp;金刚上师2个小时的授课，睿智大爱普度众生。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 399px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">　　第二天一早出发去<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">大理</a>，队员们到周城亲身体验白族扎染艺术的制作过程。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EA/51/wKgBZ1mxS72AOQp2AADRg6xqfRs77.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 399px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">　　然后&nbsp;徒步、<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">自驾</a>、骑自行车、骑电瓶车……，任意选择一种，在洱<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">海西</a>岸的田园间游行，您会深深被苍山与洱海之间的这片田园风光陶醉<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EA/51/wKgBZ1mxS76AHs-PAACtDC7ptHk85.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 399px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">　　我们在田野里骑行者，&nbsp;一片片金黄的稻谷，一排排深绿的柳树，一株株泛黄的杨树，一簇簇粉红的波斯菊花、一幢幢灰瓦白墙的白族民居，在眼前涌动<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EA/52/wKgBZ1mxS76AcLHfAAC2Kqb7fe444.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 400px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EA/52/wKgBZ1mxS7-AYmurAADWI78RoN462.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 399px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">　　以及在田间劳作的农人和或徒步或骑车的游人，形成一幅优美的风景大片。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EA/52/wKgBZ1mxS7-ABBXnAADgbpe2xdU04.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 399px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EA/53/wKgBZ1mxS7-ADu9UAACgEsGM4aM95.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 399px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">　　看过雨后低云赠予的一道接一道的彩虹，拼色相接的麦田，路上擦肩行者的微笑；有人说这是执拗的探索，可这是我用最直接的方式去体会所见的色彩<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EA/54/wKgBZ1mxS7-AcvDaAADSeRkLeg093.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; height: 399px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">　　太阳赋予大地的温度，人们善意的微笑；毋容置疑，这就是我想要探索生命的方式。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 138, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px;\"></a></p><p><br/></p>',2,'2017-09-08 14:15:21','尝试骑行从香格里拉出发，到达丽江再到大理，满眼的秋意盎然','1504880120.jpeg',20,0,0),(14,0,'<p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">起初，我对<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">蒙古</a>国没有概念，因为一直以为，<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">蒙古</a>族是<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">中国</a>少数民族，所以<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">蒙古</a>应该属于<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">中国</a>的一部分。回想童年看奥运射箭比赛，画面里的<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">蒙古</a>选手在夺冠后并非奏唱《义勇军进行曲》，那时才知道原来<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">蒙古</a>族在祖国外也有一个独立的国家，叫<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">蒙古</a>国。于是，我对“一族两国”的国家都颇有兴趣，譬如<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">朝鲜</a>、<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">蒙古</a>、<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">越南</a>…..终于在15年，完成了自己出国的第一个心愿——<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">朝鲜</a>。时隔2年后，第二个心愿来了——<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">蒙古</a>国。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_237792274\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/A0/26/wKgBZ1mb-s-ANaOOAAW-4U-479s97.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_paragraph_1\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><h2 class=\"t1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 22px; height: 86px; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/t1.gif&quot;) 0px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-weight: normal;\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 95px; display: block;\">| 奇葩出签 |</span></h2></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;出国第一关永远是签证，但我的出签之路，出奇麻烦。没想到15年在护照上的<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">朝鲜</a>签证，会给带来那么大的麻烦。由于，我是坐飞机去的<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">朝鲜</a>，走的是机场海关，因此护照上会留下签证页（坐火车去给的是临时过境纸，因此护照不留签证页）。估计是全球都在制裁<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">朝鲜</a>，加之我的护照也没有他国签证，因此大使馆总会以“动机不明”的理由将我拒签。待第五次时，我拜托旅行社为我办理“团签”，就是以旅行社的名义办理签证，这样就不存在“动机不明”的理由，但还是遭遇到了困难。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_237822874\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B3/25/wKgBZ1mcFJeAPedFAAULRtX5wUI06.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;在我即将出发的前两天，旅行社给我电话，说<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">蒙古</a>国正在国庆，所以那几天没法给我批签，得需要我改期并提交一份日程表给大使馆。那时内心是焦虑的，因为错过<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">蒙古</a>国国庆，就等于错过了那达慕大会，那是<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">蒙古</a>国一年一度的盛世，在那里你会看见骑马、摔跤、射箭、歌舞等传统项目。但虽然是错过了，不过签证还是批下来了。接下来就是买火车票了。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_237798161\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/A3/A1/wKgBZ1mb_lmAVRMvACLPr3V-pYs87.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 680px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_paragraph_2\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><h2 class=\"t1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 22px; height: 86px; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/t1.gif&quot;) 0px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-weight: normal;\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 95px; display: block;\">| “懵擦”购车票 |</span></h2></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;对于旅游的人，可能更希望去一些路线完善或是耳熟能详的国度，譬如<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">越南</a>、<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">泰国</a>、<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">菲律宾</a>、<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">马来西亚</a>、<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">新加坡</a>等，有些国家基础建设虽不完善，但一套套超详细攻略等着一批批旅客前仆后继。也有些国家，由于发达、公共基础服务建设，即便没有攻略都足够让你拿着地图走遍各地。但<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">蒙古</a>国，去的大多数都是“跟团”旅客，来也匆匆去也匆匆，除了留下一堆合照，也就什么都没了，而且网上也没有攻略可以借鉴。因此，计划这趟旅行和在这个国家的点滴，都得用我蹩脚的英语和指手画脚的功夫去刨根问底，就譬如说“买火车票”这么简单的事儿……</p><div id=\"_j_photo_237798546\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 138, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative; zoom: 1;\"></a></div><p><br/></p>',2,'2017-09-08 14:18:17','蒙古国，不和谐的存在','1504880296.jpeg',40,1,0),(15,0,'<div id=\"_j_paragraph_1\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><h2 class=\"t1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 22px; height: 86px; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/t1.gif&quot;) 0px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-weight: normal;\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 95px; display: block;\">八月照相馆：我的人生四季</span></h2></div><div id=\"_j_photo_238563882\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, 