; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-weight: normal;\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 95px; display: block;\">这里是贝加尔湖</span></h2></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">想去<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">贝加尔湖</a>的愿望很简单，甚至有点老土。所谓四季有时，夏看荷花、冬看雪，秋季的枫叶和春天的河水，这大抵就是我所能想到一年四季之中最美好的事物了。自从来到<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">杭州</a>，结识了一个叫做董舒子的同学，我就总是被她拉着在恰当的时间做恰当的事。就连冬天去看雪，似乎都变得顺理成章了起来。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_238301381\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/C3/2F/wKgBZ1mdnK2ADbQAABqlty-gOaE15.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px; padding-left: 0px;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"_j_anchor\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>安加拉河</a></span></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">天唱（左）：全程被蒙在鼓里的被求婚girl，和舒子一起担任自此旅行策划以及摄影。中文系双鱼座，养了一只叫做汤圆的龙猫和一个叫做书童的男朋友。本篇游记撰写者。<br/><br/>董舒子（右）：又称海蒂。2015年夏天，我们相识于蜂窝里的一篇<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">柬埔寨</a>游记。在刚来到<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">杭州</a>的第一年里能相识这样的好友是特别幸运的一件事儿。两个女生总有说不完的话拍不完的照和一场又一场期待的旅行。我们在同一个月里接到登上蜂首的通知，一起度过了两个春夏秋冬，一起探讨更多的人生可能。而如今，由她策划的一场求婚之旅已经发生，赠我一场旅行和回忆，大概没有什么比这更炫酷的事情了吧，以后的以后我都将把这段故事深埋在回忆深处。这里省略万言感谢。哦对了，为了更加有纪念意义，她还特意赶在我和书童领证的日子里发表了她的<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">贝加尔湖</a>游记，游记传送门：<a href=\"http://undefined\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px;\">http://www.mafengwo.cn/i/6581546.html</a></p><div id=\"_j_photo_235688520\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F5/D6/wKgBZ1mUUKGAQeuHAAt9dZJ2iSI92.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">▲&nbsp;波波：海蒂的老朋友，常常出现于她的游记中。未见其面，先闻其人，直到后来成了我们家龙猫汤圆女儿的麻麻，我们才有了更直接的关系。说好的甩手掌柜，却责无旁贷地成为本次旅行的活地图，在<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">俄罗斯</a>这样的非英语国家，竟然可以麻溜儿的找到公交站，带我们穿街过巷，行动力满分。很御姐。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_235688716\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F6/81/wKgBZ1mUULeAemnLAApLv4aD6Bo08.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">▲&nbsp;Lena：网瘾少女兼管账少女，以绝对聪明的头脑和出其不意的言论，被我们封上“金句王”的称号。理工科出身的Lena算得一手好账，做得一手好表格，让我特别崇拜。而且她还是第一位将我们的旅行游记写出来的姑娘，你有多特别就有多可爱，游记都忍不住多看几遍。游记传送门：<a href=\"http://undefined\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px;\">http://www.mafengwo.cn/i/6581699.html</a></p><div id=\"_j_photo_235690243\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/FB/A0/wKgBZ1mUUVWAECMjAAvKkWYFPW865.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 448px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">▲&nbsp;闪闪：这位在<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">湖南</a>游记里就与我一路相随的girl，在这次旅行里被大家一致授予“手机灵魂P图手”的荣誉。一个字儿“美”！喝伏特加如同喝白开水，是一位特别热心特别容易满足并且很能够感染身边人的开朗姑娘。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_236825437\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F2/C2/wKgBZ1mY39SARL2qACYApQFoZ-I22.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">▲&nbsp;书童：生活里的磊总，游记里的小书生。此次求婚事件男主角。漂洋过海、一路相随，直到掺和进了五个女人中间。对生活和我保持着诗一般的热情。（咦，我是不是在撒狗粮~）</p><div id=\"_j_photo_238254351\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/AA/2F/wKgBZ1mdhmiACPukABse63cXGGo63.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 382px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">▲&nbsp;感谢遇到你们。</p><div id=\"_j_paragraph_3\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><h2 class=\"t1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 22px; height: 86px; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/t1.gif&quot;) 0px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-weight: normal;\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 95px; display: block;\">chapter 1：【初遇】这里很热</span></h2></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">在来到<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">贝加尔湖</a>之前，我曾想象和憧憬着它的样子。<br/>这里是苏武独守数十载的<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">北海</a>，是契诃夫笔下透过水面就像透过空气一样，温柔碧绿的水色。<br/><br/>冬天冰雪满地，海水深蓝，透着晶莹的光亮。<br/>我无法形容第一次见到它的震撼与感动。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_236528080\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"></a></div><p><br/></p>',2,'2017-09-08 14:19:34','如果，有人在贝加尔湖向你求了婚','1504880373.jpeg',28,0,0),(16,7,'<p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">云南</a>，曾经是我对旅行的所有幻想。<br/>单单说出这个名字，脑海中就已是大片的蓝，大朵的云，<br/>热闹的小镇，还有小镇里穿着斑斓民族服饰的女子，<br/>穿城而过的冉冉流水，<br/>以及，无数个美好的仿佛飘在空中的日子。<br/>写<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">贵州</a>的游记时曾经写下“似乎想要到达的地方总是难以到达”，如今却也能豪迈的说一句“想到达的地方，终有一日会在眼前”。<br/><br/>时间，以飞快的速度划过眉梢，<br/>百转千回终于与你相遇，<br/>我早已不是那个独独憧憬着<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">云南</a>的小姑娘，却也庆幸，是此刻与你相遇。<br/><br/><br/>▍|▍▍||▍|▍|▍▍||▍|▍|▍▍||<br/></p><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><br/>是<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">成都</a>的八月，风扇忙碌的摆着脑袋，黑黑发来消息问要不要一起去<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">云南</a>，<br/>大概我就是这样的一个人，只要是喊着出去玩的话，总能一瞬间被勾引到，虽然嘴<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">上犹</a>犹豫豫，心里早已开始盘算着预算和路线了~<br/>于是，就在一个稀松平常的日子，去<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">云南</a>便被很轻易的提上日程了。<br/><br/>也会唏嘘，<br/>曾经约好的一起，曾经吵着闹着，曾经计划充足，都未曾成行的<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">云南</a>，<br/>却在如今，一念之间。<br/>说出来不免矫情，但似乎很多事都是如此，时过境迁后竟想不起来当时阻拦自己的究竟是什么，而后将之归于“缘分”二字。<br/><br/>我与<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">云南</a>的缘分，大概就是如此。<br/></p><div id=\"_j_photo_235304096\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;