 142, 142);\">昆明</a><br/>D12&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">昆明</a>【滇池-海埂公园】—&nbsp;<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">成都</a><br/><br/></p><div id=\"_j_paragraph_2\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/83/FF/wKgBZ1mg5DqAGkVVAAPY07PXA9U63.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fh%2F150%2Fq%2F90\" class=\"no_word _j_anchor\" title=\"—  初见  昆明记忆  —\" alt=\"—  初见  昆明记忆  —\"/></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">在近40度湿热的<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">成都</a>奔跑着赶上了去<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">昆明</a>的火车，一夜便到<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">昆明</a>。<br/>早晨10点的<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">昆明</a>，风吹在脸上是丝丝凉意，虽是熙熙攘攘的火车站，却也觉得无比清爽。<br/>跟着人流出站，抬头便是浅蓝色的天空和卷舒着的云朵。<br/></p><div id=\"_j_photo_233912837\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/D5/7D/wKgBZ1mOTLKAcA09AAg2TcM9H8o43.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"_j_anchor\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"traffic\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) -100px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>昆明站</a></span></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">因为打算乘当天晚上11点多到<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">大理</a>的火车，所以直接把行李寄存在火车站存包处，一件行李存一天10块钱~<br/>存好包后便出发去翠湖公园与<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">云南</a>大学，在火车站对面乘坐公交直达翠湖公园。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_233912838\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"_j_anchor\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>翠湖公园</a></span></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">下车后饥肠辘辘的在路边吃了鸡丝米线，到<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">云南</a>后的第一顿必须是米线哇~<br/>还蛮喜欢路边的小店，一般都不会令人失望的~<br/><br/>吃过饭后向前没走多久，便到了翠湖公园。<br/><br/></p><div id=\"_j_paragraph_3\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F3/FB/wKgBZ1msCMiAeAbuAAFas8P6_6045.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fh%2F150%2Fq%2F90\" class=\"no_word _j_anchor\" title=\"· 翠湖公园\" alt=\"· 翠湖公园\"/></div><div id=\"_j_photo_233912839\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/D5/A1/wKgBZ1mOTNSAXMt_AArmNoEqzPI18.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 457px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"_j_anchor\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>翠湖公园</a></span></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">八月下旬的<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">昆明</a>，风和日丽的午后，就这样突然站在了翠湖公园的门口，旅行的迷人之处总在于此。<br/>昨日还是一群人在<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">成都</a>的艳阳里挥汗如雨，今日便踩在这片如春的土地上了。<br/><br/>翠湖公园，是<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">昆明</a>市区最漂亮的公园之一，这里曾是滇池的一个湖湾，后因水位下降而成一<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">汪清</a>湖。<br/>每年冬季会有大量红嘴鸥飞到这里过冬。<br/>之前有收到大学室友冬季拍到的红嘴鸥，傻傻的是极可爱的。<br/>时至初秋，我们自然是看不到萌萌哒的红嘴鸥了，不过也不曾遗憾，有什么就享受什么~</p><div id=\"_j_photo_233912840\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/D5/BC/wKgBZ1mOTOqAWbapAAsZi68h83s88.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"_j_anchor\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>翠湖公园</a></span></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">在湖边见到带学生出来写生的老爷爷，<br/>一直以来都是极羡慕会画画的人，巧手一动便成画卷。<br/>将钟爱的美景一笔一划，跃然纸上，真是件极浪漫的事。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_233912841\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/D5/EC/wKgBZ1mOTQeAGz8gABBK4CwzELM40.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"_j_anchor\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>翠湖公园</a></span></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">虽说是初秋，在春城却丝毫看不到一丝萧瑟，绿柳仍是一片盎然。<br/>两人是格外的闲适，把一切眼前的景致收尽眼底，脚下是轻快的步伐，心上是无闲事的好时节。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_233912842\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/D6/00/wKgBZ1mOTRSABRt8AAZH97n8FL052.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"_j_anchor\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; verti