tyle: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">喀纳斯</a>是挨着很近的，所以第三天的安排相对是最紧凑的。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_230908755\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://a1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/07/18/wKgBZ1mCmkaAKJu1ABZWPbCjKTE83.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 382px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">禾木</a>公路，<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">新疆</a>最美三大公路之一，沿途的风景可以说是看不够，遗憾的是没有带航拍，不然出片又是另一种感觉。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_230909480\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: r