PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">这家分店是东城根上街店，离人民公园只有几十米的距离。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_228004415\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/32/FD/wKgBZ1l2tRuAbFMeAAoxQ4Pgpt033.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 680px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"_j_anchor\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"food\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) -50px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>小名堂担担甜水面(东城根上街店)</a></span></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">吃完小名堂就去人民公园了，本地气息很浓的地方，能看到跳广场舞的，游船的，散步的，能感受到<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">成都</a>的“慢生活”。不需要门票。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_228120330\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 138, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative; zoom: 1;\"></a></div><p><br/></p>',1,'2017-09-08 14:36:39','蓉城印象，成都五天四晚深度游（详细行程定制与美食推荐','1504881398.jpeg',15,0,0),(21,7,'<div class=\"post_info\" style=\"padding-left: 3px; word-wrap: break-word; float: left; width: 600px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><div class=\"a_con_text cont\" id=\"pnl_contentinfo\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); line-height: 24px; font-size: 14px;\"><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">重庆</a>有着绝美的夜景、火辣的火锅、漂亮的美女，活脱脱一个火辣辣的城市。不仅有山、水、林、泉、瀑、峡、洞等为一体的自然风光,也拥有丰富的历史文化景观,<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">重庆</a>的语言于饮食文化也是极大的特色。<br/>在<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">重庆</a>的时候住的一家在洪崖洞旁边的青旅&nbsp;&nbsp;37度2艺术青年旅舍&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;老板是地道的<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">重庆</a>人，完全是个<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">重庆</a>通，给我们讲了好多<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">重庆</a>的玩的吃的。我们基本上就按老板说的在体验。<br/><br/>D1<br/>解放碑——<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">三峡</a>博物馆——李子坝——鹅岭二厂——洪崖洞<br/>D2<br/>涂鸦街——李子坝——鹅岭二厂——鹅岭公园<br/>D3<br/>洋人街——下浩<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">老街</a>——精典书店——南山——南滨路——长江索道<br/>D4<br/>解放碑——<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">大学城</a>（美院）——磁器口——皇冠大扶梯——山<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">城步</a>道<br/><br/>如果还有什么想去的地方，就去<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">重庆</a>周边游走一下<br/><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">武隆</a>仙女山&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br/><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">黑山</a>谷奥陶纪&nbsp;<br/>&nbsp;北碚<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">偏岩古镇</a><br/>更多美丽的地方等你去发现<br/><br/><br/>D1<br/>解放碑——<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">三峡</a>博物馆——李子坝——鹅岭二厂——洪崖洞<br/><br/>解放碑：八一好吃街、人民公园掏耳朵、国泰大剧院(<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">重庆</a>美术馆)如果有展览可以去转转<br/>&nbsp;<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/49/BD/wKgBZ1ms2AGAJu8AAAJha1SnNK024.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 400px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/4A/96/wKgBZ1ms2VGAPzPZAAQWUCyjowE76.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 450px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;<br/>&nbsp;<br/><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">三峡</a>博物馆：解放碑有多路公交可以直接到达，去<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">重庆</a>人民大礼堂和<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">三峡</a>博物馆&nbsp;在一块地方（博物馆周一闭馆，请注意时间出行）<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/49/C3/wKgBZ1ms2BCAf_dIAAB0jkNPyqo07.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 300px; width: 534px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;<br/><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">洪雅</a>洞：适合晚上去19：30开灯，23:00关灯，（最好不要在洪崖洞吃&nbsp;主食，味道一般）<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/48/CA/wKgBZ1ms1heAT6xHAAsEKm48k8k81.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 399px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br/>逛完洪崖洞，晚上还可以坐&nbsp;&nbsp;两江夜游轮船（船票68—200元多不等），换个角度看<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">重庆</a><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/>D2<br/>涂鸦街——李子坝——鹅岭二厂——鹅岭公园<br/><br/>涂鸦街：&nbsp;川美老校区，黄桷坪校区交通茶馆和涂鸦街<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/49/FA/wKgBZ1ms2FmAPLLwAAF99FHUaEM97.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 450px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;<br/><br/>李子坝：2号线轻轨站点(穿楼而过的轻轨站)<br/><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 400px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;<br/>鹅岭二厂：李子坝站往山上走，穿过往上的楼梯，15分钟左右，就可以到达鹅岭二厂场文创园（从你的全世界路过拍摄地）&nbsp;，还有一家网红咖啡馆——懒鱼时光咖啡馆(适合拍照）<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 450px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">鹅岭公园：晚上，就在二厂旁边的鹅岭公园可以鸟瞰<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">重庆</a>夜景，公园里有个高塔（门票5元）登塔上顶，视野非常开阔(个人认为比一棵树性价比高）<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 399px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br/><br/><br/>D3<br/><br/>洋人街——下浩<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">老街</a>——精典书店——南山——南滨路——长江索道<br/><br/>洋人街：公交乘坐公交去洋人街(适合拍照也是个游乐园)有世界上最大的厕所<br/><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 367px; width: 490px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;<br/>下浩<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">老街</a>:另一个即将消失的十八梯，<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">老街</a>老巷，<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">重庆</a>最原始的生活味道<br/><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 450px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 800px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">精典书店：<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">重庆</a>文化地标，从1998年成立以来一直引领着这个城市的阅读生活，是一个写书人与读书人交汇的聚集地<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 301px; width: 465px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;<br/>&nbsp;<br/>&nbsp;<br/>&nbsp;<br/>南山：山上在黄桷垭<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">老街</a>&nbsp;有&nbsp;&nbsp;三毛故居&nbsp;.老君洞&nbsp;（老君洞的天王殿顶层可以鸟瞰<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">重庆</a>山城全景，关键是免费，开放时间8:00——17:30)<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 450px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 450px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;<br/>南山一棵树：<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">重庆</a>最大的山顶观景平台，最适合拍夜景（尽量避免周末去，人太多）<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 334px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;<br/>南滨路：<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">重庆</a>最美的滨江路，拥有大型音乐喷泉，一路风景秀丽，夜景超美<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 398px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;<br/><br/>长江索道：乘坐的时候最好是从南岸（<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">龙门</a>浩站点）往解放碑方向，南岸区站点一般不用排队，解放碑新华路站点乘坐人员一般都很多。<br/><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 400px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;<br/>D4<br/>解放碑——<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">大学城</a>（美院）——磁器口——皇冠大扶梯——山<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">城步</a>道<br/><br/><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">大学城</a>：<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">大学城</a>(川美的<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">马赛</a>克墙)罗中立美术馆。川美湖区沿湖廊道<br/><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 366px; width: 550px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;<br/>磁器口：去磁器口(乘坐地铁1号线到磁器口站下车，咖啡店&nbsp;麻花&nbsp;）&nbsp;&nbsp;，大冰的小屋&nbsp;（沙坪坝区磁器口横街金碧桥2号）<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 449px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;<br/>皇冠大扶梯：地铁1号线或轻轨3号线两路口站出来就到了<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 280px; width: 500px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;<br/><br/>山城第三步道：入口在中兴路法院旁边，上口在<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">重庆</a>七星岗地铁站附近<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 399px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><br/><br/>4-5天后，就可以去周边了，有一日团可以报<br/><br/><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">武隆</a>仙女山<br/><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">黑山</a>谷奥陶纪玻璃栈道<br/></p></div><div class=\"integral\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 10px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; width: 500px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(229, 110, 2); position: relative;\"><div class=\"legend\" style=\"padding: 5px 10px; word-wrap: break-word; position: absolute; left: 30px; top: -15px;\">获得积分</div><a href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(229, 110, 2); cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"cursor: pointer;\">发表游记</span><span style=\"color:#e56e02\"><span style=\"cursor: pointer;\">&nbsp;</span></span><strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); cursor: pointer;\">+30</strong><span style=\"color:#e56e02\"><span style=\"cursor: pointer;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;文章被回复&nbsp;</span></span><strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); cursor: pointer;\">3</strong></a></div></div><div class=\"clear\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; clear: both; height: 0px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"></div><p><br/></p>',1,'2017-09-08 14:38:30','重庆，非去不可（重庆自由行路线攻略）','1504881509.jpeg',32,1,0),(22,6,'<div id=\"_j_paragraph_1\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><h2 class=\"t1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 22px; height: 86px; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/t1.gif&quot;) 0px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 95px; display: block;\">0 日：那些有的没的</span></h2></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;时隔多月，终于动手整理春节<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">俄罗斯</a>的这段旅程。<br/><br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;翻开&nbsp;@<a href=\"http://undefined\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">你大佬周Sir</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;的《西伯利亚之冬，<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">贝加尔湖</a>之蓝》。这篇游记是缘起、是指引，再见是温故、是对比、是再一次发现。<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;不一样的视角下，西伯利亚展现出完全不同的面貌，给予旅行者的感受是如此不同。相信换个时间再重走一遍，也会是另一次别样的旅途。每个旅程都是一次独一无二，无法复写。<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;记下属于我的西伯利亚之行。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_237454922\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 600px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/A7/C6/wKgBZ1ma13iAHZH7AAAlAQvijNo13.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 50px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;春节<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">北京</a>飞往<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">伊尔库茨克</a>的机票一夜骤涨，虽然出行预算额外增加，但却给了我乘坐国际联运火车的出行选择，西伯利亚铁路便是此行最美好的意外。<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">贝加尔湖</a>的行程完全参考@<a href=\"http://undefined\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">你大佬周Sir</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;的建议，在奥利洪岛安排了3个整日，加上头尾往返总共5天。火车抵达<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">伊尔库茨克</a>要比伙伴们晚一天，最终放弃<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">利斯特维扬卡</a>，将有限的时间留给了<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">伊尔库茨克</a>。<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;故，此篇游记也将分为“西伯利亚大铁路”及“<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">贝加尔湖</a>”两段。</p><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">Part。1&nbsp;▷▷▷▷▷▷<br/>D1:&nbsp;Shanghai&nbsp;-&nbsp;Beijing&nbsp;<br/>D2:&nbsp;K19&nbsp;(Beijing&nbsp;-&nbsp;Shenyang&nbsp;-&nbsp;Haerbin)&nbsp;<br/>D3:&nbsp;K19&nbsp;(Manzhouli&nbsp;-&nbsp;Zabaikal&#39;sk&nbsp;-&nbsp;Hilok)&nbsp;<br/>D4:&nbsp;K19&nbsp;(Ulan-Ude)&nbsp;-&nbsp;Irkutsk&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br/></p><div id=\"_j_photo_215547661\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/6B/8B/wKgBZ1k5iNGANdcoAB2qIkSzmDg64.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 749px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_237454925\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 600px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/A7/CC/wKgBZ1ma13qAaSMfAAAlWv_jjDM46.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 50px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">※两机两镜，6D&nbsp;+&nbsp;1635mmF4&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;450D&nbsp;+&nbsp;24105mmF4&nbsp;。<br/>※脚架。火车上没什么用到，且我蠢得又忘了拿云台……<br/><br/>but，在一个几乎空荡无人的封闭环境里，拍什么呢？急速行驶的列车，弱光的环境，无法推开的脏窗子……<br/>一切的不利因素，通过不断地摸索、尝试拍出自己颇为满意的照片，为火车旅行平添乐趣。<br/></p><div id=\"_j_photo_237454927\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 600px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/A7/CD/wKgBZ1ma13qAQnkPAAAn5vKxCtQ54.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 50px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">行前就充分考虑了下怎么打发火车上的时间，<br/><br/>※发呆是必然的<br/>※背景音乐绝对不可缺<br/>※两本和西伯利亚没什么关系的书《<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">京都</a>的门外汉》、《永恒的时光之旅》<br/>※旅程“相关”电影两部。《我在故宫<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">修文</a>物》大电影及《中俄列车大劫案》。哈~<br/></p><div id=\"_j_photo_237456265\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 600px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/AE/B9/wKgBZ1ma2FaAWcfZAAA0rhR9EXk74.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 50px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">西伯利亚流放始于16世纪末，沙俄统治者在占领西伯利亚后,即把那里确定为新的流放地。在随后的300多年的时间&nbsp;里,大批的刑事犯<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">和政</a>治犯被流放到西伯利亚。然而无论是作为惩罚措施,还是移民手段,抑或是为了排除对其统治的威胁,西伯利亚流放都显得微不足道。1917年二月革命后,随着沙皇专制制度的覆灭,西伯利亚流放制度被最终废除了。<br/><br/>然从地理上看，西伯利亚西起<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">乌拉尔</a>山脉，东迄太平洋，北临北冰洋，西南抵<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">哈萨克斯坦</a>中北部山地，南与<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">中国</a>、<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">蒙古</a>和<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">朝鲜</a>等国为邻，面积1276万平方千米。&nbsp;它虽地广人稀，幅员辽阔，但物产资源丰富。<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">俄罗斯</a>科学家、作家<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">罗蒙诺索夫</a>曾经说过：“<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">俄罗斯</a>的强大在于西伯利亚的富饶。”<br/><br/>这里虽然是一块曾经的流放之地，但不荒芜、更非不毛之地。</p><div id=\"_j_paragraph_2\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><h2 class=\"t1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 22px; height: 86px; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/t1.gif&quot;) 0px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 95px; display: block;\">1 日：启程</span></h2></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">大年初一，说新年好，说再见，一路向北。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_215547662\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/6B/8C/wKgBZ1k5iNKAdQEWAAUKTLMOTOI56.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 392px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"_j_anchor\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"traffic\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) -100px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>北京站</a></span></div><div id=\"_j_photo_215547663\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/6B/8C/wKgBZ1k5iNKAAmS9AAV5tHSnNFw85.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 439px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"_j_anchor\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"traffic\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) -100px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>北京站</a></span></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">上次到<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">北京</a>站还是09年元旦。那次因大雪航班取消，改火车回<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">上海</a>。恰逢<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">北京</a>站正大修，再加上一路赶时间狂奔，不曾注意<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">北京</a>站到底长什么样。这次K19要晚上23点发车，有足够的时间看看这个老<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">北京</a>站。<br/><br/>这个时刻的<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">北京</a>站，没有拥挤吵杂的人群，没有数不清的现代化检票口，多了一份出行前的惬意。<br/><br/>春节乘坐这趟跨国列车的人实在不多。满打满算也就30来人，而从<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">北京</a>到<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">满洲里</a>段，国际车厢就我和另一傻妞……包车的赶脚真好=&nbsp;v=</p><div id=\"_j_photo_215547664\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/6B/8C/wKgBZ1k5iNOAVNzxAAcES5wbF6I81.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 430px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"_j_anchor\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"traffic\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) -100px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>北京站</a></span></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">19/20次列车全部由俄铁承运，名为“ВОСТОК”（俄语东方的意思），即“东方号”列车。<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">北京</a>出发，经<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">满洲里</a>、<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">赤塔</a>去<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">莫斯科</a>，总里程长达八千九百余公里，运行时间长达6天6夜。这条线路既是革命年代先辈们乘火车去苏联学习先进经验的“红色秘密交通线”，也是新<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">中国</a>成立之初毛主席第一次访问苏联时，乘专列所经过的路线。选择乘坐19次列车去<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">俄罗斯</a>，可以算是跟着先辈的足迹沿西伯利亚铁路旅行，也是一次难忘的“红色之旅”。<br/><br/>K19算是一条西伯利亚支线，一直到<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">赤塔</a>才并入主线。此行只走了半程，到<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">伊尔库茨克</a>3夜3天3796公里，虽不算是完全走西伯利亚铁路，但也略微体验了一把长途火车生活~<br/></p><div id=\"_j_photo_233844283\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B8/87/wKgBZ1mNxXeARV0NABG2OZ5ZInk84.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 481px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"_j_anchor\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"traffic\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) -100px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>北京站</a></span></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">19/20次国列开行至今，已经几易车体和涂装。2007年之前，列车是蓝、白、红三色的<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">俄罗斯</a>国旗涂装，同时车体上涂有俄文“东方号“字样。2008年更换为空调车体，涂装也改为棕色，车厢上标有醒目的中文“<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">莫斯科</a>-<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">北京</a>”字样。But！现在，列车已经更换为俄铁的标准涂装。<br/></p><div id=\"_j_photo_233844284\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B8/8C/wKgBZ1mNxXmAM0i7ABRF6KXOxZk61.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 410px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;\"><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"_j_anchor\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"traffic\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) -100px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>北京站</a></span></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><br/>这次定的是双人高包车厢。根据度娘的介绍此为型号61-4174的高级软卧车，定员18人，车身标注“МЕСТ-18”（俄语，读音/mʲest/，音“灭死特”，义为“定员18人”）=__,=<br/>By&nbsp;the&nbsp;way，当我发现整个国际车厢被我和土土菇凉两个人包了的时候，超后悔……早知道定个最便宜的票，那也是包车的节奏啊！</p><div id=\"_j_paragraph_3\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><h2 class=\"t1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 22px; height: 86px; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/t1.gif&quot;) 0px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\"></h2></div><p><em></em><br/></p>',1,'2017-09-10 07:29:23','【向北。P1】西伯利亚铁道上的三日谈','1505028561.jpeg',12,0,0),(23,6,'<div id=\"_j_paragraph_1\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><h2 class=\"t1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 22px; height: 86px; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/t1.gif&quot;) 0px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 95px; display: block;\">说些无关的</span></h2></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">人生有三个坡，上坡，下坡，没想到。——《四重奏》<br/><br/>产假进入倒计时，经历了分娩之痛，月子之苦，终于回归日常的时候，奶娃陪玩成为了生活的主要部分。于是，不想做一个只围着孩子转的妈妈的我做了一个谁也没想到的决定，把刚满三个月的宝宝托付给家人，开始了这场旅行。<br/><br/>有人说，旅行真正的欲望是出走。而轻井泽，恰是最让人无法招架的出走胜地。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_220577150\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/10/FA/wKgBZ1lSCj2AJN-lAA8CwDDvDYg07.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 1020px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_paragraph_2\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><h2 class=\"t1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 22px; height: 86px; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/t1.gif&quot;) 0px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 95px; display: block;\">说些有关的</span></h2></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">在出发之前，我查了很多网站，发现很少有关于轻井泽的游记或攻略，说到底这并不是一个有很多景点值得记录的地方，但她像一个混血儿，有点欧式的小资，有点日式的清新，有一种独特的气质吸引着我。<br/><br/>但另外一个更重要的原因，便是想探访一下日剧《四重奏》的取景地，就像有的人因为《情书》爱上了<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">小樽</a>，有人因为《灌篮高手》而憧憬<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">镰仓</a>一样，我因为《四重奏》而迷恋上了这里。<br/><br/></p><div id=\"_j_paragraph_3\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><h2 class=\"t1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 22px; height: 86px; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/t1.gif&quot;) 0px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 95px; display: block;\">第一天 @轻井泽</span></h2></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">进入正题，其实从<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">东京</a>到轻井泽非常方便，在上野站搭乘<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">新干</a>线一个小时左右就到了。<br/><br/>tips：<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">新干</a>线费用5180日元／人／单程，可买自由席，基本都有空位，班次也比较多，基本20-30分钟就有一班，所以不需要提前购票。当然，也可以买10000日元的jr&nbsp;pass，往返都包括在内。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_220577188\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/11/7C/wKgBZ1lSCrqAMW2IAA4v1m7djg437.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">一下车看到的蓝天白云犹如童话般美好。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_220577189\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://a4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/11/7F/wKgBZ1lSCryAequ7ABU14DG1GSc25.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_220577190\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/11/81/wKgBZ1lSCr6Aba7iABNQdUdrqT096.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top