ay: block;\"/></a></div><p><br/></p>',1,'2017-09-10 14:02:24','出水芙蓉，水中睡莲','1505052143.jpeg',40,0,0),(27,7,'<div class=\"va_con _j_master_content\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><div id=\"_j_paragraph_1\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative;\"><h2 class=\"t2\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 22px; height: 86px; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/t2.gif&quot;) 0px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: center;\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 95px; display: block;\">一、写在前面</span></h2></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;这是第三次到<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">绍兴</a>了，第一次还是在遥远的大学时代，班级组织的集体活动；二年前的春天来了第二次，和单位同事相约的，几乎逛遍了<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">绍兴</a>的大小景点；这一次，陪老人逛的，老人从<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">西北</a>来，就想看看鲁迅故里，所以一切依老人的兴趣和体力而定，自己只是随手拍上几张，无法考虑其完整性或者其他。</p><div id=\"_j_paragraph_2\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative;\"><h2 class=\"t2\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 22px; height: 86px; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/t2.gif&quot;) 0px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: center;\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 95px; display: block;\">二、兰亭</span></h2></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;位于<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">绍兴</a>城西南13公里的兰渚山麓。春秋时越王勾践种兰于此，汉代建有驿亭，兰亭由此得名。东晋<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">永和</a>九年，大书法家王羲之邀集41位文人雅士在此举行<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">曲水</a>流觞的盛会，并写下了“天下第一行书”——《兰亭集序》，因此被尊为书圣，兰亭也因此成为书法圣地。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_243803747\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B6/2C/wKgBZ1m1OGuAZVVFAAREbMiCGDs13.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 434px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_243803748\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B6/2D/wKgBZ1m1OGyAMJCsAAQNVz8uaps96.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 451px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_243803749\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B6/2E/wKgBZ1m1OG2AG0K7AAYH8C2EtjU80.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;鹅池碑亭，亭呈三角形，上镌“鹅池”两字，相传为王羲之、王献之父子合笔，故肥瘦有别。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_243804056\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B6/4F/wKgBZ1m1OJCAfJ6IAAZWRJO9B7o70.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_243804057\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 595px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B6/50/wKgBZ1m1OJGAC98uAALNzeQdEYo72.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 850px; width: 595px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;兰亭碑亭，碑高1.73米，宽1.02米，厚0.27米，碑上“兰亭”二字，系<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">清康</a>熙帝手迹。“文革”期间碑被砸断，劫后余生，遂成残字。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_243804339\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B6/68/wKgBZ1m1OK-AOVTvAAPos3kieKU23.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_243804340\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 603px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B6/69/wKgBZ1m1OLCAIZnjAALBx-GLVTo82.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 850px; width: 603px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">曲水</a>流觞，清代移建，1980年重建。长78米，宽0.8米，再现<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">永和</a>九年（公元353年）王羲之邀友临流泛觞的场景。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_243804548\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B6/7F/wKgBZ1m1OMuACCo6AAXJREANuYw71.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;御碑亭，始建于<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">清康</a>熙年间，1983年重建。碑阳镌康熙帝所书《兰亭集序》，碑阴刻乾隆帝游兰亭时所写《兰亭即事》诗，祖孙皇帝手迹同处一碑，世所罕见。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_243804681\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B6/98/wKgBZ1m1OO2AddHWAAXec0AqPXY10.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_243804682\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 609px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B6/98/wKgBZ1m1OO6AOTTcAAOUTuH0B1E96.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 850px; width: 609px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;园区很大，考虑到老人的体力，没有继续游览。即便如此，所到之处都是翠绿一片。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_243804943\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B6/BD/wKgBZ1m1ORaAO1URAAUvLr5-30w44.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_243804944\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B6/BD/wKgBZ1m1ORaAIccAAAWssrAxlSw50.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_243804945\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B6/BE/wKgBZ1m1OReABpswAAQIv_MPuD407.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_243804946\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B6/BF/wKgBZ1m1ORiAMhjuAARPCZKfrw850.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_paragraph_3\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative;\"><h2 class=\"t2\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 22px; height: 86px; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/t2.gif&quot;) 0px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: center;\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 95px; display: block;\">三、鲁迅故里</span></h2></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;从兰亭到鲁迅故里驱车约30分钟，到达时为中午时分，停车场已是车满为患，大约经过了20多分钟的排队等候，才得以进入停车场。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_243805458\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B6/ED/wKgBZ1m1OUGAbOzZAAUbualB-_w74.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;景区位于鲁迅中路，一条独具<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">江南</a>风情的历史街区。其主入口位于鲁迅中路和中兴南路口，沿鲁迅中路从东往西走，有鲁迅祖居、三味书屋、鲁迅故居、鲁迅纪念馆等。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_243805823\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/22/wKgBZ1m1OYeAEj3pAAOJK3skm4g73.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 413px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_243805824\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/24/wKgBZ1m1OYeAXTs5AARvcbvuIO842.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_243805825\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/25/wKgBZ1m1OYiAYxXjAAPtmy1_m5Q71.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;鲁迅祖居（周家老台门），系鲁迅祖辈世居之地，建于清乾隆十九年（1754年），为<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">绍兴</a>目前保存最为完好的台门建筑。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_243806092\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/48/wKgBZ1m1OauAZKIRAAMF8EICM5k90.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;鲁迅故居（周家新台门），鲁迅青少年时代生活、学习、工作的地方，1881年9月25日，鲁迅诞生在此。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_243806361\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/71/wKgBZ1m1OcmAJONDAAOgxul8quA14.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;鲁迅纪念馆，鲁迅祖居西侧，用大量实物、照片、手稿、书信、图表等，展现鲁迅生平事迹及一生的思想发展历程。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_243806475\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/93/wKgBZ1m1OemAD5vtAAPVzNZrqpo33.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_243806476\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/94/wKgBZ1m1OemAC3H6AAK9jHNIc_c25.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_243806477\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/95/wKgBZ1m1OeqAf2gIAALvS3FHHoo64.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;除展示与鲁迅相关的景点外，鲁迅中路两侧有众多的店家，大多售买各式<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">绍兴</a>土特产。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_243806981\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/BC/wKgBZ1m1Og6AfP_OAALG_qXjU-Y81.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 459px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_243806982\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/BC/wKgBZ1m1Og6AWyotAALoYRF4BEM64.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_243806983\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/BD/wKgBZ1m1Og-AW7ZqAAQ1tNhzXUk32.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div></div><div class=\"vc_total _j_help_total\" style=\"margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 15px; word-wrap: break-word; border-top: 1px solid rgb(226, 226, 226); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\">本篇游记共含942个文字，26张图片。帮助了<span class=\"_j_total_person\" style=\"font-weight: inherit;\">15</span>名<span class=\"_j_total_mdd\" style=\"font-weight: inherit;\">绍兴</span>游客。</div><p><br/></p>',1,'2017-09-10 14:04:59','浙江绍兴】从兰亭到鲁迅故里','1505052298.jpeg',35,0,0),(28,7,'<div id=\"_j_paragraph_1\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><h2 class=\"t9\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 24px; height: 50px; background: 0px center; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: 50px;\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 50px; display: block;\">前期准备</span></h2></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">1.早就知道<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">泰国</a>有一个跳傘的基地在<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">芭提雅</a>，之前跟姐說的時候，她還說想不到<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">芭提雅</a>有如此正經的活動。（正經臉）<br/>2.早確定要去泰國的時候就先在携程定了票，票基本上都是包去酒店接送到基地的。一般有兩趟，早上7-8點，中午11-12。建議都是7-8點的那趟，為什麼？看下去你就知道了。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_243781679\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/AA/AE/wKgBZ1m1KZGAAnXpAA0Ykyj0Bjc34.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_243781676\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/AA/AC/wKgBZ1m1KY-AEh3HAA98GS3HYyk74.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_paragraph_2\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><h2 class=\"t9\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 24px; height: 50px; background: 0px center; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: 50px;\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 50px; display: block;\">到達基地</span></h2></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">經過1個小時左右的車程終於到達基地，基地不大，有酒店也有固定在這附近練習跳傘的學員們，還有一個射擊場一個餐廳，其他地方只能用荒涼來形容了。在接待處問完你要跟拍要vedio還是兩個都要的安排之後，&nbsp;就去到一個小房間拿一個像我們吃飯等待的號一樣，等待。我到達的時候是12點左右，居然要安排到5點半！沒錯！我要等5個小時！！<br/>教練都調戲我們說可以回去<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">芭提雅</a>吃個飯再回來了。<br/>我以為會講一講一些注意事項之類的，結果就是等到4點多差不多上飛機了，&nbsp;教練才講了幾句。嗯，在他們眼裡，跳傘和吃飯一樣簡單。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_243781669\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/AA/AA/wKgBZ1m1KY2AXYddAAr2-5hWWmg27.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">遇到一個小販賣的椰子雪糕，點讚。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_243781691\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/AA/AF/wKgBZ1m1KZOAI7waAA2xieuxSUs18.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_paragraph_3\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><h2 class=\"t9\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 24px; height: 50px; background: 0px center; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: 50px;\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 50px; display: block;\">上機</span></h2></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">好不容易等到5點多，就上小飛機了。飛機坐了6個人，我和教練還有跟拍，外加另一個朋友的教練和跟拍。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_243789198\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/AC/4A/wKgBZ1m1LCWAZxWQAAOr94jA-jw97.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">然後就是飛啊飛啊飛上去，我超喜歡這張照的，從我video裡面截取的，感覺像是要去觸摸這個世界一樣。有一天我也要自己跳。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_243781718\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/AA/B2/wKgBZ1m1KZqALeHVABZ9LvQYvTg45.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">我是完全不緊張的，相反我後面的小夥伴就緊張多了，教練叫他把頭揚起來好多次他都緊張到忘記了。哈哈哈。我完全很enjoy的跳下，一開始開傘教練還跟我說welcome&nbsp;to&nbsp;Thailand&nbsp;。在空中看人和建築由小變大到最後，甚至還有點感謝是在下午時分去跳，我還跟教練說好開心可以看到美麗的夕陽和它的餘暉。下來后，我跟教練說——thanks&nbsp;for&nbsp;saving&nbsp;my&nbsp;life.哈哈哈<br/><br/>下面是後面小夥伴拍的視頻</p><div class=\"add_video _j_seqitem \" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 680px; height: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><video src=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/rest/app/note/video/B6A226B0AD5B315B9C33DC5901307461?jsondata=%7B%22data_style%22%3A%22direct%22%7D\" width=\"680\" height=\"420\" controls=\"controls\" class=\"_j_videoplayer\"></video></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">想好的姿勢啊什麼的都沒有用到啊，因為被吹成狗啊，手都沒法合上。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_243781736\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/AA/B6/wKgBZ1m1KZ-AJ4myABiEdxAQzmg34.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_paragraph_4\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><h2 class=\"t9\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 24px; height: 50px; background: 0px center; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: 50px;\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 50px; display: block;\">寫在最後</span></h2></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">最後拿了這張證書。同機的小夥伴說他再也不敢玩了（他後來吐了）我估計是我神經比較大條吧，一點感覺沒有，很好，我可以接下來繼續去玩啦。或許，考個證？</p><div id=\"_j_photo_243781709\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"http://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/AA/B1/wKgBZ1m1KZaAcEwDAA5RyhlDbLA60.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">完整版視頻如下：</p><div class=\"add_video _j_seqitem \" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 680px; height: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">就這樣，我也是一個上過天，下過海的人了。<br/>忽然想起一句詞——等到風景都看透，也許你會陪我看細水長流。<br/>雖然不知道你什麼時候會出現，但我人生的軌跡并不會因你的不出現而有所停滯。<br/>我的To&nbsp;list&nbsp;裡面又有一個可以劃掉了。<br/>To&nbsp;be&nbsp;a&nbsp;better&nbsp;me.</p><p><br/></p>',1,'2017-09-10 14:07:04','泰国芭提雅跳伞sky diving','1505052423.jpeg',33,0,0),(29,7,'<p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">阔别这里已有将近五年光景，这几年经历了怀孕生子创业……写第一篇游记的时候根本没有想到能再静下心来写一篇旅行记居然需要等待五年。<br/><br/>终于把孩子盼到了上幼儿园，终于可以为自己计划一次出游，没有了曾经的那种兴奋和少女式的幻想，没有了一丝不苟的行程攻略，没有了沉重的单反相机，唯有<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">平和</a>淡然之心伴我踏上旅程。时间让每个人成长，身为人母、妻子、女儿多重身份，责任感真的越发重大，把孩子托付于父母这几日也是下了很久的决心。<br/><br/>如果路途没那么遥远，更偏爱坐高铁，任凭高速的列车带我们驶向未知的远方，能毫无负担的享受这几个小时是何等的幸福。看着窗外蔓延至天边的无尽绿色，耳畔持续的轰鸣都变的悦耳。多希望在车上的时光可以再慢一点再慢一点，让我肆无忌惮的去感受在路上的美好。<br/><br/>这次去<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">杭州</a>是一拍脑门子的决定，周一上午决定，晚上买到了车票，周三早上踏上旅程。大概看了下<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">杭州</a>地图，简单了解了城市布局规划，计划去<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">杭州</a><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">乌镇</a><a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">上海</a>，具体时间还没有确定，只定了离西<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">湖南</a>宋御街比较近的酒店一晚，其他的就随机发挥，随心所欲吧<br/><br/>全程摄影只用到了iPhone6&nbsp;plus，没有相机的负担真的非常轻松，对于夜景的噪点只能忍受一下啦。</p><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><br/>DAY1.<br/>2017.8.23（周三）<br/>从<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">北京</a>南到<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">杭州</a>东，早上八点多有一班只比我们定的G165早十几分钟，却提前一小时到站，建议坐高铁的一定要买那趟，不过五个多小时的高铁时光感觉也很快就过去了。<br/></p><div id=\"_j_photo_238273607\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/09/E9/wKgBZ1mc0F-ARQudAA4kGaYHUJg15.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_238273622\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: