quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">窗外的风景还不错，放下行李我们就前往西湖，7路车一站地就到，付款用了支付宝的公交支付码，非常方便，后续坐公交一直用到，强烈建议大家绑定一个。眼看西湖越来越临近了，却感觉没有想象中的那么梦幻，哈哈像个有<a href=\"http://undefined\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">大湖</a>的公园，加之湖旁太阳光非常强烈，简单拍了几张照片我们就撤了。路过了【inWe】甜品店，买了冷泡茶，味道还挺新奇，28一杯。</p><div id=\"_j_photo_238282313\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B9/58/wKgBZ1mdk5KAVloSAA5b9LV7QCQ15.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></div><div id=\"_j_photo_238282358\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\"https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B9/5F/wKgBZ1mdk5qACs2HAA5Hx1s2A7A28.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90\" alt=\"\" sty