></span></div><div id=\"_j_paragraph_5\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><h2 class=\"t9\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 24px; height: 50px; background: 0px center; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: 50px;\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 50px; display: block;\">“随缘”，酒香不怕巷子深。</span></h2></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">出来贝壳楼一路向前，走到一户农家院门口，被干净的院子里精心铺设的石子路和桂树竹林吸引，停下了脚步，因为不确定是经营啥的院子，老爸说进去看看，我也紧随其后。院中无人，屋内走出一对打扮朴实的农家夫妇，热情的问我们有啥需要，老爸随便问了句“能吃饭吗？”，老夫妻爽快的回答“可以！”。老爸是个喜欢根据面相做决定的“处女座”，一看老板很朴实，院子屋里又整洁如新，便留下来准备吃午餐。没想到啊，这一吃，便吃出了“惊喜”。阿姨的手艺令人叫绝，菜品量大味美，海鲜鲜嫩回味无穷。自家种的蔬菜简单热炒，清淡爽口。不多说，上图：<br/></p><div id=\"_j_photo_243781447\" class=\"add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://undefined\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"_j_lazyload\" src=\