eft;color:#009900;\">耿达这里没有喧嚣的人群，只有静寂的群山；</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	<span style=\"text-align:left;color:#009900;\">这里没有沉重的雾霾，只有通透的蓝天；</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	<span style=\"text-align:left;color:#009900;\">这里没有繁忙的工作，只有畅快的行走。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	<span style=\"text-align:left;color:#009900;\">我们总是喜欢用顺其自然来敷衍生活的坎坷，</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	<span style=\"text-align:left;color:#009900;\">却很少承认，真正的顺其自然，</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	<span style=\"text-align:left;color:#009900;\">其实是竭尽所能后的不强求，而非两手一摊的不作为。</span><span style=\"color:#009900;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;\"><img src=\"/web/kindeditor/attached/image/20171205/20171205152130_88317.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	本次活动最小的一个小帅哥，他的年龄只有5岁，他坚强的毅力感染了我们所有的徒友！\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	相信只要坚持，没有完不成的目标，人生就是要挑战不可能的自己！\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	<img src=\"/web/kindeditor/attached/image/20171205/20171205152153_22472.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	<img src=\"/web/kindeditor/attached/image/20171205/20171205152257_69338.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	天苍苍，野茫茫，风吹草地见牛羊\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	<img src=\"/web/kindeditor/attached/image/20171205/20171205150527_45127.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"850\" height=\"638\" title=\"\" align=\"\" />\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	徒步两小时到了山顶，大家都被眼前的美景所吸引\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	置身于此，放佛人间仙境\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	<img src=\"/web/kindeditor/attached/image/20171205/20171205150837_25525.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"850\" height=\"638\" title=\"\" align=\"\" />\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	<img src=\"/web/kindeditor/attached/image/20171205/20171205151140_49460.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"850\" height=\"638\" title=\"\" align=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	<img src=\"/web/kindeditor/attached/image/20171205/20171205151219_62480.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"850\" height=\"638\" title=\"\" align=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	<img src=\"/web/kindeditor/attached/image/20171205/20171205151323_32482.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"850\" height=\"567\" title=\"\" align=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	<img src=\"/web/kindeditor/attached/image/20171205/20171205151352_65396.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"850\" height=\"477\" title=\"\" align=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	<img src=\"/web/kindeditor/attached/image/20171205/20171205151422_10947.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"850\" height=\"638\" title=\"\" align=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	<img src=\"/web/kindeditor/attached/image/20171205/20171205151620_22805.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"850\" height=\"638\" title=\"\" align=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	<img src=\"/web/kindeditor/attached/image/20171205/20171205151654_19168.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"850\" height=\"638\" title=\"\" align=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	<img src=\"/web/kindeditor/attached/image/20171205/20171205152324_60724.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	<span style=\"text-align:center;white-space:normal;\">一直喜欢一句话，“越努力，越幸运”，感谢能在路上相遇的你们。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	<img src=\"/web/kindeditor/attached/image/20171205/20171205151059_41667.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"850\" height=\"638\" title=\"\" align=\"\" />\n</p>',2,'2017-12-05 06:25:18','12月2日活动游记 l走进耿达熊猫坪--看川西美景、野马、草甸、雪山、彩林、','1512458712.jpg',18,0,0);
